(36, 'tt2916318', 1, 'The Star', 'MV5BMjk3OTU1MDk3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAxMzcyNzE@', 'With Akbari dead, Carrie and Brody try to get to a safe house and wait for extraction.', 3, 12, '15 Dec. 2013'),
(37, 'tt3284012', 1, 'The Drone Queen', 'MV5BMTU2NjkyNTc3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY2MTA4MjE@', 'Carrie makes a crucial decision after learning pressing intelligence; Saul struggles to adjust to his new role in the private sector.', 4, 1, '5 Oct. 2014'),
