(40, 'tt3505186', 1, 'Iron in the Fire', 'MV5BOTQzODA3NzA3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk4ODYyNzE@', 'Carrie gets a tip from Redmond regarding Quinn''s lead. Saul calls in a favor with an old friend in the Pakistani military. Fara uncovers a deep-rooted conspiracy.', 4, 4, '19 Oct. 2014'),
