(73, 'tt0562992', 2, 'Rose', 'MV5BMjAwMDQwMjMxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAyNDEzMjE@', 'Rose Tyler is just an ordinary shop worker living an ordinary life in 21st century Britain. But that life is turned upside down when a strange man calling himself The Doctor drags her into an alien invasion attempt!', 1, 1, '17 Mar. 2006'),
(74, 'tt0562997', 2, 'The End of the World', 'MV5BMjA1ODUzNDI2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor takes Rose to the year 5 billion to witness the destruction of the Earth.', 1, 2, '17 Mar. 2006'),
(75, 'tt0563001', 2, 'The Unquiet Dead', 'MV5BMTU2OTI2NTMyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDgxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor has great expectations for his latest adventure when he and Rose join forces with Charles Dickens to investigate a mysterious plague of zombies.', 1, 3, '24 Mar. 2006'),
(76, 'tt0562985', 2, 'Aliens of London', 'MV5BMjI2MTUwMjA0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor returns Rose to her own time - well, sort of - but her family reunion is ruined when a spaceship crashes in the middle of London. What is the origin of the spaceship, and where has the Prime Minister gone in this time of crisis?', 1, 4, '31 Mar. 2006'),
(77, 'tt0563003', 2, 'World War Three', 'MV5BMTQ4MjY5MTY4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIxNDEzMjE@', 'The fiendish Slitheen have been unmasked as the ones who crashed the spaceship into London as part of a ruse to trigger World War Three. But how can The Doctor save the planet when he''s trapped inside a locked room?', 1, 5, '7 Apr. 2006'),
(78, 'tt0562988', 2, 'Dalek', 'MV5BMzI4OTIwODYzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTcxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Rose travel to the year 2012 and land in a museum of extra-terrestrial objects accumulated by the very wealthy Henry van Statten. He''s an avid collector - the TARDIS lands on the museum''s 53rd floor below ground level - but he''s also using ', 1, 6, '14 Apr. 2006'),
(79, 'tt0562999', 2, 'The Long Game', 'MV5BMjQxNDE5ODMxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI5NzA3NTE@', 'The Doctor and Rose arrive in the year 200,000 to see The Fourth Great and Bountiful Human Empire. But something has gone wrong - someone is holding back the development of mankind. Who could have done this? And why?', 1, 7, '21 Apr. 2006'),
(80, 'tt0562989', 2, 'Father''s Day', 'MV5BMzc3NzIyOTQzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTUxNDEzMjE@', 'All of her life, Rose''s mother told how great a man her father Pete was. He was killed by a hit and run driver when Rose was just a baby and among her many regrets was that her father died alone, just lying on the street. Rose asks the Doctor to take her ', 1, 8, '28 Apr. 2006'),
(81, 'tt0562996', 2, 'The Empty Child', 'MV5BMjE5Njk5OTAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTkxNDEzMjE@', 'Rose and the Doctor find themselves in 1941 London when the TARDIS receives an emergency signal from another time-traveling vehicle. While the Doctor tries to determine where the object may have landed, Rose goes off in search of a child she can hear call', 1, 9, '5 May 2006'),
(82, 'tt0562995', 2, 'The Doctor Dances', 'MV5BMTY1ODIyMTgzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor, Rose and Captain Jack Harkness are still in the hospital with the gas mask-wearing mutants and are having some trouble finding a way out. The Doctor determines that the ambulance Captain Jack was using in his scam contained nano genes, similar', 1, 10, '12 May 2006'),
(83, 'tt0562987', 2, 'Boom Town', 'MV5BMjQ1OTk4NDYwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTMxNDEzMjE@', 'Stopping off in present-day Cardiff to recharge the TARDIS, The Doctor, Rose and Jack encounter an old foe in the midst of hatching a scheme that could destroy the entire planet.', 1, 11, '19 May 2006'),
(84, 'tt0562986', 2, 'Bad Wolf', 'MV5BMjYwMjg0NTk3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDkxNzU5NTE@', 'Jack, The Doctor and Rose have been kidnapped and forced to play terrible and deadly games. But what happens to the bodies of the murdered contestants? And what sinister plot do the games hide?', 1, 12, '2 Jun. 2006'),
(85, 'tt0563000', 2, 'The Parting of the Ways', 'MV5BMTQ3MjQ0NTc0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEyNDEzMjE@', 'The Dalek fleet is poised to destroy the Earth and only The Doctor, Rose, Jack and a band of television producers can stop them.', 1, 13, '9 Jun. 2006'),
(86, 'tt0562994', 2, 'The Christmas Invasion', 'MV5BMjM5ODQ5NDcwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjcxNDEzMjE@', 'It''s Christmas Eve, but this is to be a far from silent night - the cruel Sycorax have come to Earth to enslave mankind and, as ever, only The Doctor can stop them. Unfortunately, he''s lying in a coma in Jackie''s home...', 2, 1, '29 Sep. 2006'),
(87, 'tt0562990', 2, 'New Earth', 'MV5BNjMwMjExNjI4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIxNDEzMjE@', 'As Rose Tyler embarks upon her first big TARDIS adventure with the newly-regenerated Doctor, they discover a sinister hospital run by strange cat people and run in to two old acquaintances, The Face of Boe and Cassandra.', 2, 2, '29 Sep. 2006'),
(88, 'tt0563002', 2, 'Tooth and Claw', 'MV5BMTYxMzE0OTg4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Rose are transported to 19th Century Scotland, where they meet Queen Victoria, and try to protect her from a ravenous werewolf and a band of assassinating warrior-monks', 2, 3, '6 Oct. 2006'),
(89, 'tt0562993', 2, 'School Reunion', 'MV5BMjE3NDgwNzIzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI1NTMwMjE@', 'The Krillitanes - aliens with a mix-and-match physiology - are trying to crack the ''God-Maker'', a paradigm to give them ultimate power. They are using children as a computer, and only the Doctor and Rose, re-united with Sarah Jane Smith and K9 can prevent', 2, 4, '13 Oct. 2006'),
(90, 'tt0562998', 2, 'The Girl in the Fireplace', 'MV5BMjYyNjcyMjUzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzUxNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor, Mickey and Rose land on a spaceship in the 51st century only to find 18th century Versailles on board, the time of Madame De Pompadour! To find out what''s going on the Doctor must enter Versailles and save Madame De Popmpadour but it turns int', 2, 5, '20 Oct. 2006'),
(91, 'tt0562991', 2, 'Rise of the Cybermen', 'MV5BMTQzMjUyMzE4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI1NTMwMjE@', 'Upon landing on an alternate version of the Earth, The Doctor, Rose and Mickey learn that Peter Tyler is apparently alive and well. Lurking in the shadows are creatures made to destroy - one of The Doctor''s greatest fears have come true...the Cybermen are', 2, 6, '27 Oct. 2006'),
(92, 'tt0756447', 2, 'The Age of Steel', 'MV5BMzIzNDI2NTc1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMjU1MTM3', 'Lumic''s army of cybermen is on the rise, and with more and more people being converted by the hour, time is of the essence. The gang are reduced to fugitives as they roam the streets of parallel London trying to rid the earth of cybermen.', 2, 7, '3 Nov. 2006'),
(93, 'tt0756451', 2, 'The Idiot''s Lantern', 'MV5BMTA2NjgwMzM5MTNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDYzMjQxMzIx', 'In 1950s London, the police are hunting down strange, mute creatures. The people of Britain gather around their new-fangled "tele-vision" sets to celebrate the new Queen''s coronation - but is something affecting the signal?', 2, 8, '10 Nov. 2006'),
(94, 'tt0772457', 2, 'The Impossible Planet', 'MV5BMTgzMjc4NDI5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA3MTIzMjE@', 'The TARDIS lands on an alien planet shrouded in a darkness that even the Doctor can''t figure out. And what is lurking at the bottom of The Satan Pit?', 2, 9, '17 Nov. 2006'),
(95, 'tt0756448', 2, 'The Satan Pit', 'MV5BMzY4MDMxNzE0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTcyNDEzMjE@', 'As Rose battles the murderous Ood, the Doctor finds his every belief being challenged to the core, as the Pit beckons. With the planet threatening to fall into the black hole, the Doctor must make the ultimate sacrifice.', 2, 10, '1 Dec. 2006'),
(96, 'tt0766171', 2, 'Love & Monsters', 'MV5BMjI0ODQwOTYxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYwNDIzMjE@', 'A run in with the Doctor at a young age leads Elton to a group who''s studying him, they become friends and have a laugh until Victor Kennedy arrives. Suddenly everything becomes more serious then people start disappearing from the group. Can the Doctor sa', 2, 11, '8 Dec. 2006'),
(97, 'tt0756446', 2, 'Fear Her', 'MV5BMjI0ODMyNzQ2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTkyNDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Rose travel to London in 2012 to see the Olympics - only to find that children are mysteriously disappearing before peoples very eyes. The answer seems to lie with a young girl named Chloe and her strange drawings - but is there something m', 2, 12, '15 Dec. 2006'),
(98, 'tt0756449', 2, 'Army of Ghosts', 'MV5BMjI5OTcyMTk0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTAyNDEzMjE@', 'As the ghosts of loved ones appear, the whole world celebrates. But as the Doctor investigates he believes that there is a more sinister motive behind their appearence. And deep within the Torchwood tower, a mysterious sphere containing the greatest enemi', 2, 13, '22 Nov. 2006'),
(99, 'tt0756450', 2, 'Doomsday', 'MV5BNzY0NTU2NTQ1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE1NTMwMjE@', 'Earth becomes the battlefield for the greatest and deadliest war of all time, as the Daleks and the Cybermen clash with the whole universe at stake. The Doctor and Rose, reunited with old friends and Cybermen experts Mickey and Jake, race to find a way to', 2, 14, '22 Dec. 2006'),
(100, 'tt0827573', 2, 'The Runaway Bride', 'MV5BMjI3NzkwNjkwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA1MTIzMjE@', 'The Doctor is baffled when a young woman is transported to the TARDIS on her wedding day, and attempts to find out how she is connected to an alien plot to destroy Earth.', 3, 1, '6 Jul. 2007'),
(101, 'tt0974728', 2, 'Smith and Jones', 'MV5BMjE4NzYzODY4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQwMTEzMjE@', 'When the hospital she works at is transported to the moon, medical student Martha Jones joins forces with The Doctor to hunt down an alien fugitive before the oxygen runs out.', 3, 2, '6 Jul. 2007'),
(102, 'tt0974729', 2, 'The Shakespeare Code', 'MV5BMTUwMDg2OTY5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjczNTMwMjE@', 'The Doctor takes Martha to London in 1599, where William Shakespeare''s new play is being used by three witches in an evil plan.', 3, 3, '7 Apr. 2007'),
(103, 'tt1000253', 2, 'Gridlock', 'MV5BMjIyNzgxOTAxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjczNTMwMjE@', 'The Doctor takes Martha to New Earth, where she is kidnapped by two carjackers and taken to an underground Motorway, where the remainder of humanity on the planet live in perpetual gridlock.', 3, 4, '14 Apr. 2007'),
(104, 'tt0993186', 2, 'Daleks in Manhattan', 'MV5BMTUwNTU3OTQyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgzMDIzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Martha travel to New York in 1930, where people have been mysteriously vanishing from the streets, and an old enemy resurfaces.', 3, 5, '21 Apr. 2007'),
(105, 'tt0996572', 2, 'Evolution of the Daleks', 'MV5BMjIwNjQ0MjMyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA4NTEzMjE@', 'Concluding part to Daleks in Manhattan. In 1930s New York, the Daleks'' plan is in full force. Faced with the cyborgs'' most evil and dangerous scheme yet, will the Doctor and Martha be able to defeat their greatest opponents?', 3, 6, '28 Apr. 2007'),
(106, 'tt1000257', 2, 'The Lazarus Experiment', 'MV5BMjYzNjk5ODA1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDA3NzEzMjE@', 'The famous Dr Lazarus has appeared to discover the secret of eternal youth - but do his experiments hide a sinister secret?', 3, 7, '5 May 2007'),
(107, 'tt1000251', 2, '42', 'MV5BMjI1NjM2MjUzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDczNTMwMjE@', 'On a spaceship headed straight for the center of the sun, The Doctor only has 42 minutes to save Martha and the rest of the ship''s crew from an inevitable doom...', 3, 8, '19 May 2007'),
(108, 'tt1000254', 2, 'Human Nature', 'MV5BMjA1NjA5NzQ5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzc2NzEzMjE@', 'In 1913, Martha watches in jealousy from afar as The Doctor learns what it is to be human and to fall in love with the local school nurse, Joan Redfern.', 3, 9, '26 May 2007'),
(109, 'tt1000256', 2, 'The Family of Blood', 'MV5BMjM5Nzk0NzI4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc2NzEzMjE@', 'The Doctor must deal with the repercussions of his decision to become human, as The Family Of Blood unveil themselves...', 3, 10, '2 Jun. 2007'),
(110, 'tt1000252', 2, 'Blink', 'MV5BMzk4NDQ3NDQzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIzNzEzMjE@', 'Sally Sparrow receives a cryptic message from the Doctor about a mysterious new enemy species that is after the TARDIS.', 3, 11, '9 Jun. 2007'),
(111, 'tt1000259', 2, 'Utopia', 'MV5BMTQwOTk0MDgyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDgzNTMwMjE@', 'Soon after bumping into old friend Jack Harkness, Martha and The Doctor head off to Malcassairo, a distant planet where an old professor will do anything he can to keep his people alive...', 3, 12, '16 Jun. 2007'),
(112, 'tt1000258', 2, 'The Sound of Drums', 'MV5BNzc2OTIzNTE5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTUzODQwNw@@', 'The Doctor, Martha and Jack return to the 21st Century eighteen months after the Doctor and Martha left. They find they''ve missed the election, and the new Prime Minister, Harold Saxon, is someone they''ve met before by another name.', 3, 13, '23 Jun. 2007'),
(113, 'tt1000255', 2, 'Last of the Time Lords', 'MV5BMTU0ODMyOTAzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODg2NzEzMjE@', 'It''s been a year since The Master unleashed the mysterious Toclafane onto Earth. With the human race and The Doctor enslaved under The Master''s control, Martha Jones is the only person that can help stop the evil Time Lord.', 3, 14, '30 Jun. 2007'),
(114, 'tt1061123', 2, 'Voyage of the Damned', 'MV5BMTk2NDA0NjMzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDUzMDIzMjE@', 'The Doctor finds his TARDIS colliding with a spaceship based on the RMS Titanic during a Christmas party. With the help of a waitress named Astrid, the Doctor must take on the race called the Hosts as the lives of the Titanic crew and those on Earth are i', 4, 1, '18 Apr. 2008'),
(115, 'tt1159991', 2, 'Partners in Crime', 'MV5BMTQ0OTUwNzU3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc2ODEzMjE@', 'With a new weight-loss pill tested in London by Adipose Industries, The Doctor goes to investigate the sinister truth behind the product, only to find out that his old friend Donna Noble is investigating as well.', 4, 2, '25 Apr. 2008'),
(116, 'tt1173173', 2, 'The Fires of Pompeii', 'MV5BMTgwMDk4MDA2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc2MzIzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Donna visit Pompeii in AD 79, on the eve of the eruption of Mount Vesuvius.', 4, 3, '2 May 2008'),
(117, 'tt1173174', 2, 'Planet of the Ood', 'MV5BMTQyNTI1NDAxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg2MzIzMjE@', 'Finding themselves on the Ood-Sphere planet in the 42nd century, The Doctor and Donna discover the truth over the Ood''s willingness to serve humankind.', 4, 4, '9 May 2008'),
(118, 'tt1159992', 2, 'The Sontaran Stratagem', 'MV5BMTgzNjU0MTQ3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc2ODEzMjE@', 'UNIT''s newest recruit Martha Jones enlists The Doctor''s help to investigate kid genius Luke Rattigan and his ATMOS system that is used in every car on Earth.', 4, 5, '16 May 2008'),
(119, 'tt1208127', 2, 'The Poison Sky', 'MV5BMTkyNTIyMDQ2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjM0NzEzMjE@', 'With planet Earth choking under the poison sky, the Doctor must stop the Sontarans'' threat to the planet.', 4, 6, '30 May 2008'),
(120, 'tt1205439', 2, 'The Doctor''s Daughter', 'MV5BMTQyOTAzMDc3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDA0ODEzMjE@', 'Caught in the middle of a war between the Humans and the Hath in the planet Messaline, the Doctor finds himself once again a father.', 4, 7, '6 Jun. 2008'),
(121, 'tt1208130', 2, 'The Unicorn and the Wasp', 'MV5BNzA3NDU1NTQxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjc0NzEzMjE@', 'With a 1920s dinner party turning into a murder mystery, The Doctor and Donna meet Agatha Christie on the eve of her publicized disappearance.', 4, 8, '13 Jun. 2008'),
(122, 'tt1208129', 2, 'Silence in the Library', 'MV5BMjAxNDkyNDEwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjgzNzEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Donna join a group of archaeologists at a 51st century library. What caused the library to become abandoned? What are the Nodes? And what links the library to one little girl? All they have is one warning - count the shadows.', 4, 9, '20 Jun. 2008'),
(123, 'tt1205440', 2, 'Forest of the Dead', 'MV5BMTkxNjQzNTY3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjczODEzMjE@', 'With the library darkening, the Doctor takes on the Vashta Nerada while figuring out what links River Song to his future. Meanwhile, Donna finds out the mystery of Dr. Moon and the Girl.', 4, 10, '27 Jun. 2008'),
(124, 'tt1208128', 2, 'Midnight', 'MV5BMTk1NjEwMDAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM0NzEzMjE@', 'As part of a well-deserved holiday, the Doctor takes a bus tour on the planet Midnight. Little does he know that something is knocking on that bus'' wall...', 4, 11, '11 Jul. 2008'),
(125, 'tt1205436', 2, 'Turn Left', 'MV5BMjEzNzg5Mzk1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkzODEzMjE@', 'What would happen if Donna never met the Doctor? How would Earth handle the Racnoss, the falling Titanic or the Sontarans? Aided by a familiar blonde time traveler, Donna corrects the alternate time line from happening.', 4, 12, '21 Jun. 2008'),
(126, 'tt1205437', 2, 'The Stolen Earth', 'MV5BMjE4MDY4NDIzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTYzODEzMjE@', 'The return of an old enemy leaves Earth along with 26 other planets stolen from their places. As the Doctor and Donna look for the whereabouts of Earth, former companions of the Doctor assemble a resistance against the new Dalek Empire.', 4, 13, '28 Jun. 2008'),
(127, 'tt1205438', 2, 'Journey''s End', 'MV5BMTcwOTgzMjI1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQzODEzMjE@', 'In the wake of Davros'' threat to destroy the existence of the Universe itself, the Doctor''s companions unite to stop the Dalek empire. Which one will die by the prophecies and what will the fate be for the Doctor?', 4, 14, '5 Jul. 2008'),
(128, 'tt1577256', 2, 'The Eleventh Hour', 'MV5BMTgzMDA4OTQ4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzU0MDU1NA@@', 'With his TARDIS in ruins, the newly-regenerated Doctor with the help of Amy Pond must save the world in less than twenty minutes from galactic policemen known as the Atraxi.', 5, 1, '17 Apr. 2010'),
(129, 'tt1577257', 2, 'The Beast Below', 'MV5BNjY3MDI5OTE3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzA0MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor takes Amy to the future inside Starship UK, which contains in addition to British explorers, an intimidating race known as the Smilers.', 5, 2, '10 Apr. 2010'),
(130, 'tt1577258', 2, 'Victory of the Daleks', 'MV5BMTc0Njk3NDg0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYwMTEzMjE@', 'The TARDIS takes The Doctor and Amy to war-torn Britain in the middle of World War Two. Not only do they meet Winston Churchill himself, but the Doctor comes face to face once again with his greatest enemy of all.', 5, 3, '17 Apr. 2010'),
(131, 'tt1577259', 2, 'The Time of Angels', 'MV5BMTMzMDE1NDY0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzY1MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor and Amy emerge from the TARDIS to find the wreck of the Byzantium spaceship. Down below the Weeping Angels are stirring, but the Doctor has someone else to contend with; none other than the mysterious Professor River Song.', 5, 4, '24 Apr. 2010'),
(132, 'tt1589021', 2, 'Flesh and Stone', 'MV5BMTg5Njk2OTI2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDE1MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor, Amy, Dr. Song and the remaining soldiers manage to escape from the crashed ship and into the forest. The Angels attempt to create a rift in time and space much as the Doctor had found in Amy''s room when they first met. Amy meanwhile is countin', 5, 5, '1 May 2010'),
(133, 'tt1591787', 2, 'The Vampires of Venice', 'MV5BNDE1OTk3Nzg3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzg1MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor and Amy cross swords in more ways than one with a horde of blood-sucking vampires in 16th century Venice.', 5, 6, '8 May 2010'),
(134, 'tt1591788', 2, 'Amy''s Choice', 'MV5BMTk3NTQzMTEwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTgzMDU1NA@@', 'Five years after finally leaving the TARDIS Amy and Rory now married, live in the quiet little village of Leadworth. But everything is not what it would seem.', 5, 7, '15 May 2010'),
(135, 'tt1591789', 2, 'The Hungry Earth', 'MV5BMjIyMjQxMTIxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTI1MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor tries to get everyone to Rio, but nothing quite goes as planned. They arrive in a small Welsh village where the Doctor immediately senses that the ground isn''t quite right. There is a drilling rig nearby that has reached a depth of 21 kilometer', 5, 8, '22 May 2010'),
(136, 'tt1591790', 2, 'Cold Blood', 'MV5BNjQ0OTQyMzg1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjI0MDU1NA@@', 'The Doctor and Nasreen Chaudry go deep underground and find an ancient society that has been disturbed by the drilling. They are gassed and taken prisoner just as Amy manages to free herself. The military commander of the underground reptilians, Restac, i', 5, 9, '29 May 2010'),
(137, 'tt1591786', 2, 'Vincent and the Doctor', 'MV5BNjg1Mjc4NzU1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQ5MzIzMjE@', 'Visiting a museum, the Doctor and Amy are especially excited with the gallery for Vincent van Gogh. Many of van Gogh pieces are displayed, including "The Church at Auvers (1890)". However there is something irregular discovered on the painting - a small a', 5, 10, '5 Jun. 2010'),
(138, 'tt1607757', 2, 'The Lodger', 'MV5BMTU0MTUwNjgwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjg1NTc1NA@@', 'No sooner does the TARDIS land on Earth that it leaves again - but without the Doctor who had just stepped outside. The Doctor soon finds himself at the home of Craig Owens, who has been advertising for a lodger. There''s clearly something odd in the house', 5, 11, '10 Jul. 2010'),
(139, 'tt1607758', 2, 'The Pandorica Opens', 'MV5BMTc4NTUyNzg2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDk1NTc1NA@@', 'River Song returns to deliver The Doctor a serious warning from his allies: the mythical Pandorica, said to contain the most feared creature in the entire Universe, is opening.', 5, 12, '17 Jul. 2010'),
(140, 'tt1607759', 2, 'The Big Bang', 'MV5BMTQyNDM5MzEyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjA2NTc1NA@@', 'The Daleks, Cybermen and others have imprisoned in the Pandorica the most dangerous creature in the universe - the Doctor, who they say will in the future destroy the universe. Moving to 1996, a preteen Amy Pond visits a museum with her Aunt and opens the', 5, 13, '26 Jun. 2010'),
(141, 'tt1672218', 2, 'A Christmas Carol', 'MV5BMTU2ODIxODM0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDgwNTMyNA@@', 'A space liner, with a large number of passengers aboard, is in difficulties while flying through the atmosphere of an unknown planet. Amy and Rory have been spending some time on board in the honeymoon suite and they quickly appear on deck. Amy calls the ', 6, 1, '25 Dec. 2010'),
(142, 'tt1723888', 2, 'The Impossible Astronaut', 'MV5BNjg2NjY1NTg2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ0MTIzMjE@', 'River Song, Rory, The Doctor and Amy are reunited in the Utah desert', 6, 2, '23 Apr. 2011'),
(143, 'tt1723889', 2, 'Day of the Moon', 'MV5BMTU1Mjk4NTUxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQ0MTIzMjE@', 'Still in 1969, the Doctor has come to the conclusion that the alien creatures are only seen when they directly look at them. As soon as you look away, any memory of their presence is wiped clean. The aliens are also able to leave suggestions in people''s m', 6, 3, '30 Apr. 2011'),
(144, 'tt1721225', 2, 'The Curse of the Black Spot', 'MV5BNTA1MDI0NjQwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzEzMDIzMjE@', 'On board a 17th century pirate ship sailing the ocean waves, a crew under the command of one Captain Avery are being picked off one by one by a ghostly apparition. They believe it to be a legendary Siren, a beautiful and mesmerizing demon who lures men to', 6, 4, '7 May 2011'),
(145, 'tt1721226', 2, 'The Doctor''s Wife', 'MV5BMTkzOTMzOTM2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEzMDIzMjE@', 'While traveling in the TARDIS with Rory and Amy, the Doctor hears a knock on the TARDIS doors. Bewildered and no doubt curious, he answers, only to be presented with a mysterious box which carries a distress signal. Believing it to be from a fellow Time L', 6, 5, '14 May 2011'),
(146, 'tt1777783', 2, 'The Rebel Flesh', 'MV5BMjAwNDA5OTkwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjU0NDEzMjE@', 'The Doctor, Amy and Rory arrive in a future Earth where a small group of humans operate a plant extracting highly dangerous chemicals. To minimize the danger to themselves, they create clones made of a plastic-like substance, ''gangers'' (short for doppelga', 6, 6, '21 May 2011'),
(147, 'tt1777782', 2, 'The Almost People', 'MV5BMjAyMTkyMTY0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE1NDEzMjE@', 'As the dopplegangers - ''gangers'' for short - fight their makers, both Doctors, the real one and his ganger, try to find a way to restore the power and get everyone off the island. Both Doctors claim to be the 100% real thing, something Emily can''t quite g', 6, 7, '28 May 2011'),
(148, 'tt1777781', 2, 'A Good Man Goes to War', 'MV5BNzg2Nzk4NTUyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTc0NDEzMjE@', 'A member of The Doctor''s team has been abducted and he will call in every favor and maybe even go to war to get him/her back.', 6, 8, '4 Jun. 2011'),
(149, 'tt1795142', 2, 'Let''s Kill Hitler', 'MV5BNjA5ODU5ODc0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU5MTIzMjE@', 'In the desperate search for Melody Pond, the TARDIS crash lands in Thirties Berlin, as the time-travelling drama returns for the second half of the series shown earlier in the year. The Doctor comes face to face with the greatest war criminal in the Unive', 6, 9, '27 Aug. 2011'),
(150, 'tt1795143', 2, 'Night Terrors', 'MV5BMjIxNTc4MzQ2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ5MTIzMjE@', 'A young boy living in a tower block on a council estate sends out, unknowingly, a psychic distress call transmitted to the Doctor''s ''psychic paper''. When the doctor and his associates eventually find the correct flat in the tower block, they are inadverte', 6, 10, '3 Sep. 2011'),
(151, 'tt1795139', 2, 'The Girl Who Waited', 'MV5BMjEyOTgxMTI1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ5MTIzMjE@', 'Amy is trapped in a quarantine facility for victims of an alien plague which could kill the doctor in minutes if he were to catch it. So Rory is the only one who can go into the facility to save her but can he save her before she is killed by kindness?', 6, 11, '10 Sep. 2011'),
(152, 'tt1795140', 2, 'The God Complex', 'MV5BMjIyNjIxODUyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQ5MTIzMjE@', 'The Doctor, Amy and Rory become trapped in a hotel of horrors unable to escape and unable to find the TARDIS. The Doctor must save as many people as he can taking many twists and seeing his own worst fear.', 6, 12, '17 Sep. 2011'),
(153, 'tt1795141', 2, 'Closing Time', 'MV5BMTY1MzY0ODMwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTQ5MTIzMjE@', 'After traveling for 200 years and leaving messages for Amy Pond across time and space, the Doctor realizes his time is up, its time to settle down and accept his future at Lake Silencio. . . . . .But not before one last goodbye. The Doctor travels to Engl', 6, 13, '24 Sep. 2011'),
(154, 'tt1824359', 2, 'The Wedding of River Song', 'MV5BNzY4MDE1NTIyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTAyMzIzMjE@', 'It''s April 22, 2011 the day the Doctor is supposed to die but time seems to be stuck at 5:02 p.m. London streets are clogged not only with automobiles but also Roman chariots; pterodactyls fly in the sky. The Holy Roman Emperor, Winston Churchill, calls o', 6, 14, '1 Oct. 2011'),
(155, 'tt1998643', 2, 'The Doctor, the Widow and the Wardrobe', 'MV5BMTYxMjkzODQzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODM4MjUxNw@@', 'It''s Christmas Eve, 1938, when Madge Arwell comes to the aid of an injured Spaceman Angel as she cycles home. He promises to repay her kindness - all she has to do is make a wish. Three years later, a devastated Madge escapes war-torn London with her two ', 7, 1, '25 Dec. 2011'),
(156, 'tt2402301', 2, 'Asylum of the Daleks', 'MV5BMTY5MjQ0NDY1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDUyNjEzMjE@', 'The Doctor along with an Amy and Rory who are headed for divorce are kidnapped by the Daleks. They find themselves before the Dalek Parliament and the Doctor is quite surprised when he learns why: they want the him to save them. A ship has crashed on the ', 7, 2, '1 Sep. 2012'),
(157, 'tt2317659', 2, 'Dinosaurs on a Spaceship', 'MV5BMTU0MjU5MTk2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzAyMzIzMjE@', 'After a lengthy absence, the Doctor returns to Earth and scoops up up Amy and Rory for yet another adventure. He also manages somehow to include Rory''s dad, Brian Williams. Those aren''t the only travelers however as Queen Nefertiti and big-game hunter Joh', 7, 3, '8 Sep. 2012'),
(158, 'tt2340501', 2, 'A Town Called Mercy', 'MV5BOTU2MDg0OTgxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzM5NDUzOA@@', 'The Doctor gets a Stetson (and a gun), and finds himself the reluctant Sheriff of a Western town under siege by a relentless cyborg who goes by the name of The Gunslinger. But who is he and what does he want?', 7, 4, '15 Sep. 2012'),
(159, 'tt2399633', 2, 'The Power of Three', 'MV5BMTQxOTk5Njc1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY1NzEzMjE@', 'Earth is suddenly visited by millions of small black cubes of unknown origin. The Doctor joins Amy, Rory and Rory''s father, Brian, to help discover what these cubes bring for humanity.', 7, 5, '22 Sep. 2012'),
(160, 'tt2378951', 2, 'The Angels Take Manhattan', 'MV5BNjA1MzAwMDEwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTYwMTIzMjE@', 'The Doctor takes Amy and Rory to New York, where the Weeping Angels are waiting for them. River Song returns.', 7, 6, '29 Sep. 2012'),
(161, 'tt2380513', 2, 'The Snowmen', 'MV5BMTkzNzMyODAwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMyMjIzMjE@', 'London, 1892. Snow is trying to evolve, feeding off of the nightmares of a little girl. But the Doctor has given up on saving the world. It is up to a young governess named Clara to convince him, with just one word, to save the day.', 7, 7, '25 Dec. 2012'),
(162, 'tt2222152', 2, 'The Bells of Saint John', 'MV5BMzI3MjczNTUyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0NDcxNDE@', 'A chance phone call reunites the Doctor with Clara in the present day. A mysterious organization, lead by the evil Miss Kizlet, sends robots known as "Spoonheads" to steal the minds of people who use the company''s WiFi. The Doctor and Clara must work toge', 7, 8, '30 Mar. 2013'),
(163, 'tt2284610', 2, 'The Rings of Akhaten', 'MV5BMjk3NzQ5ODk2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjc2MzIzMjE@', 'Still not quite able to explain just who she is, the Doctor and Clara set off on their first adventure. He takes her to see the Rings of Akhaten and its famous pyramid. The residents of the 7 planets rotating around the same sun all believe the pyramid is', 7, 9, '6 Apr. 2013'),
(164, 'tt2267312', 2, 'Cold War', 'MV5BMTQyODcxNjAwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjU2NjEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Clara find themselves dealing with Cold War tensions when the TARDIS lands aboard a disabled Soviet ballistic submarine. The Doctor isn''t the only alien being on board however - while engaged in undersea drilling, Professor Grisenko thought', 7, 10, '13 Apr. 2013'),
(165, 'tt2267332', 2, 'Hide', 'MV5BMjEzMzA0ODgwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODM5NDEyOQ@@', 'The Doctor and Clara arrive at an old manor house in 1974 where Alec Palmer and Emma Grayling are investigating the existence of a ghost. Alec is a former army Major, now a psychologist, whilst Emma is an empathic psychic who can not only sense the presen', 7, 11, '20 Apr. 2013'),
(166, 'tt2267326', 2, 'Journey to the Centre of the TARDIS', 'MV5BMTk1NDEyMTM1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY1NjEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Clara find themselves aboard a space freighter that has taken the TARDIS on-board as salvage. While the Doctor is ejected, Clara finds herself wandering through the vehicle exploring it''s many - seemingly infinite - rooms. The Doctor re-ent', 7, 12, '27 Apr. 2013'),
(167, 'tt2204480', 2, 'The Crimson Horror', 'MV5BMjAwNjY4NDg0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ3MzEzMjE@', 'The Doctor and Clara arrive in 19th century Yorkshire where moral crusader Mrs Gillyflower is recruiting beautiful people for her idyllic garden city. At the same time rigid corpses dyed red are piling up and the brother of one of the victims seeks help f', 7, 13, '4 May 2013'),
(168, 'tt2267338', 2, 'Nightmare in Silver', 'MV5BMTY3NDk5Mzc4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc1NjEzMjE@', 'Hedgewick''s World of Wonders was once the greatest theme park in the galaxy, but it''s now the dilapidated home to a shabby showman, a chess playing dwarf and a dysfunctional army platoon. When the Doctor, Clara, Artie and Angie arrive, the last thing they', 7, 14, '11 May 2013'),
(169, 'tt2267346', 2, 'The Name of the Doctor', 'MV5BMjMyNjcwNTAyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU1NjEzMjE@', 'The Doctor''s friends are being kidnapped, which leads him to the fields of Trenzalore, where his greatest secret will be revealed and Clara''s mystery will be solved.', 7, 15, '18 May 2013'),
(170, 'tt3469416', 2, 'Deep Breath', 'MV5BMjI0NTgxNTI4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY1NDc5MjE@', 'When the newly-regenerated doctor arrives in Victorian London, he finds a dinosaur rampant in the Thames and a spate of deadly spontaneous combustions.', 8, 1, '23 Aug. 2014');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `imdb_id`, `serie_id`, `title`, `poster_id`, `summary`, `season`, `episode`, `air_date`) VALUES
(171, 'tt3737226', 2, 'Into the Dalek', 'MV5BMjE2MDI5MTcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQyNTc5MjE@', 'The Doctor and Clara find themselves inside of a supposedly good Dalek.', 8, 2, '30 Aug. 2014'),
(172, 'tt3714112', 2, 'Robot of Sherwood', 'MV5BMTQ2NzIzNDUwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODE0NTc5MjE@', 'In Sherwood forest, the Doctor finds an evil plan from outer space and makes an alliance with Robin Hood. With Nottingham at stake, the Doctor must decide who is real and who is fake.', 8, 3, '6 Sep. 2014'),
(173, 'tt3745430', 2, 'Listen', 'MV5BMTc5Mjc3NTY1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODcyNTc5MjE@', 'When ghosts of past and future crowd into their lives, The Doctor and Clara are thrown into an adventure that takes them to the very end of the universe.', 8, 4, '13 Sep. 2014'),
(174, 'tt3845940', 2, 'Time Heist', 'MV5BMzMyOTQwNTAxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODUyMTg5MjE@', 'The Doctor and Clara must break into the most secure bank in the universe.', 8, 5, '20 Sep. 2014'),
(175, 'tt3845938', 2, 'The Caretaker', 'MV5BMjMxNjc2NDA5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY1MTg5MjE@', 'The terrifying Skovox Blitzer is ready to destroy all humanity - but worse, and any second now, Danny Pink and the Doctor are going to meet.', 8, 6, '27 Sep. 2014'),
(176, 'tt3787384', 2, 'Kill the Moon', 'MV5BMjIyMjQ0NDUwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzEzMjg5MjE@', 'In the near future, the Doctor and Clara find themselves on a space shuttle making a suicide mission to the Moon. Crash-landing on the lunar surface they find the most terrible things.', 8, 7, '4 Oct. 2014'),
(177, 'tt3787400', 2, 'Mummy on the Orient Express', 'MV5BMTg5OTUwMTE1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQzMTg5MjE@', 'On the most beautiful train in history, speeding amongst the stars of the future, a deadly and immortal creature is stalking the passengers.', 8, 8, '11 Oct. 2014'),
(178, 'tt3834038', 2, 'Flatline', 'MV5BMTEwNTM2MDAwMjVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDQ5OTMwMTMx', 'A problem happens with the Tardis, trapping the Doctor inside and leaving Clara to fend for herself against a two dimensional enemy.', 8, 9, '18 Oct. 2014'),
(179, 'tt3834040', 2, 'In the Forest of the Night', 'MV5BMjQwMjA0NDM1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE4ODcxMzE@', 'One morning in London, and every city and town in the world, the human race wakes up to the most surprising invasion yet: the trees have moved back in. Everywhere, in every land, a forest has grown and taken back the Earth.', 8, 10, '25 Oct. 2014'),
(180, 'tt3834042', 2, 'Dark Water', 'MV5BMTQ0MDc2MDgwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAyNTUzMzE@', 'In the mysterious world of the Nethersphere, plans have been drawn. Old friends and old enemies manoeuvre around the Doctor, and an impossible choice is looming over him.', 8, 11, '1 Nov. 2014'),
(181, 'tt3834044', 2, 'Death in Heaven', 'MV5BMjE5MTc5NzQ4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzk3ODgzMzE@', 'With Cybermen on the streets of London, old friends unite against old enemies and the Doctor takes to the air in a startling new role. As the Doctor faces his greatest challenge, sacrifices must be made before the day is won.', 8, 12, '8 Nov. 2014'),
(182, 'tt4050552', 2, 'Last Christmas', 'MV5BMTQ4MjYwMjE2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIwNzE3MzE@', 'The Doctor and Clara face their Last Christmas. Trapped on an Arctic base, under attack from terrifying creatures, who are you going to call? Santa Claus!', 9, 1, '25 Dec. 2014'),
(183, 'tt4289846', 2, 'The Magician''s Apprentice', 'MV5BMTkyODYyNzczOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIzMzk1NjE@', 'When the skies of Earth are frozen by a mysterious alien force, Clara needs her friend, the Doctor. But where is he and what is he hiding from?', 9, 2, '19 Sep. 2015'),
(184, 'tt4464958', 2, 'The Witch''s Familiar', 'MV5BNTcyNDJhYzUtZGM1ZS00MjA2LWE0NTUtYmYwZTMxMjhmYzBlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTI2ODA1NQ@@', 'Trapped and alone in a terrifying Dalek city, the Doctor is at the heart of an evil Empire; no sonic, no TARDIS, nobody to help. With his greatest temptation before him, can the Doctor resist? And will there be mercy?', 9, 3, '26 Sep. 2015'),
(185, 'tt4483506', 2, 'Under the Lake', 'MV5BNDdjZTBjN2QtZWFmMC00ODIyLTgzMmUtM2FkMDVlMThjYTUyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTI2ODA1NQ@@', 'Under a lake a gleaming black spaceship is recovered but there is nothing inside. When the base crew start dying, they discover that ghosts are real. The Doctor and Clara arrive to find the base under siege and the Doctor discovers that this is more than ', 9, 4, '3 Oct. 2015'),
(186, 'tt4483520', 2, 'Before the Flood', 'MV5BODY2NzgyNzY5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ1NzYwNzE@', 'In a town that never was, the Doctor and his friends are being stalked by a mysterious figure. With the past and future in the balance, can the Doctor stop the evil Fisher King? And more importantly, who composed Beethoven''s 5th.', 9, 5, '10 Oct. 2015'),
(187, 'tt4507160', 2, 'The Girl Who Died', 'MV5BY2IzZTljOWQtZTA3Mi00OTk3LTk1ZmQtNWI3NWIyMTU0YjczXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTI2ODA1NQ@@', 'In a Viking village, a girl named Ashildr is about to make a desperate mistake. The Mire are the deadliest mercenaries in the galaxy, famed for showing no mercy and Ashildr has just declared war on them. The Doctor and Clara have 12 hours to turn a peacef', 9, 6, '17 Oct. 2015'),
(188, 'tt4545140', 2, 'The Woman Who Lived', 'MV5BMjI2Mjk0ODYyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjA4MjA3NjE@', 'England, 1651. A deadly highwayman known only as ''The Knightmare'' plagues the dark streets of London, his fire-breathing accomplice by his side. There''s something clearly more than human here, and that includes the loot as much as the outlaws. Who are the', 9, 7, '24 Oct. 2015'),
(189, 'tt4652840', 2, 'The Zygon Invasion', 'MV5BNTQxNzU3NzI3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA4MjA3NjE@', 'The fragile peace between the Humans and the Zygons is on a knife edge. Tensions run high as factions within the Zygon community seek to incite violent action against Humans. Called in by UNIT, the Doctor and Clara fight to bring he situation under contro', 9, 8, '31 Oct. 2015'),
(190, 'tt4652846', 2, 'The Zygon Inversion', '01', 'With the Zygons invading England, and UNIT neutralized, the Doctor stands alone to stop the Zygons from taking over the entire planet. But how can he stop the Zygons? And how can he save his friends?', 9, 9, '7 Nov. 2015'),
(191, 'tt4787004', 2, 'Sleep No More', 'MV5BNTQ2Mjk2MTE1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjg5MjgyNzE@', 'Vision recovered from the wreckage of Le Verrier Space Station shows how the Doctor and Clara became entangled in a rescue mission. As the footage plays out, a horrifying secret is uncovered.', 9, 10, '14 Nov. 2015'),
(192, 'tt4701538', 2, 'Face the Raven', 'MV5BMTkwNzUxNDczOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjA0ODIzNzE@', 'The Doctor and Clara are called back to earth when Rigsy discovers a strange tattoo on the back of his neck that appears to be counting down to zero. Their investigation leads them to a hidden street in the middle of London, the discovery that Rigsy has b', 9, 11, '21 Nov. 2015'),
(193, 'tt4701542', 2, 'Heaven Sent', 'MV5BODc4Nzg0NjczNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODEzOTczNzE@', 'Trapped in a world unlike any other he has seen, the Doctor faces the greatest challenge of his many lives. One final test. And he must face it alone...', 9, 12, '28 Nov. 2015'),
(194, 'tt4701544', 2, 'Hell Bent', 'MV5BODY4OTY3NjYwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTM0OTczNzE@', 'If you took everything from him, betrayed him, trapped him, and broke both his hearts... how far might the Doctor go? Returning to Gallifrey, the Doctor faces the Time Lords in a struggle that will take him to the end of time itself. Who is the Hybrid? An', 9, 13, '5 Dec. 2015'),
(195, 'tt4701546', 2, 'The Husbands of River Song', 'MV5BYmQ3ZTgxMWYtZmNlOS00Y2Y1LWE0YTEtNmViMWM4ZTRhNDBlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEzNjA2NzM@', 'When a crashed spaceship calls upon the Doctor for help, he finds himself recruited into River Song''s squad and hurled into a chase across the galaxy.', 10, 1, '25 Dec. 2015'),
(196, 'tt5163494', 2, 'Episode #10.1', '01', 'Add a Plot', 10, 2, '25 Dec. 2016'),
(197, 'tt0170817', 3, 'Pilot', 'MV5BMTkyMjc3NzY0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDEwNzg3MjE@', 'Agent Dana Scully is instructed to debunk an FBI project dubbed "The X-Files," paranormal cases that have been reopened by Agent Fox Mulder.', 1, 1, '10 Sep. 1993'),
(198, 'tt0751099', 3, 'Deep Throat', 'MV5BNzIzNTIzMDY0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzMzNzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully investigate the mysterious case of a military test pilot who disappeared after experiencing strange psychotic behaviour.', 1, 2, '17 Sep. 1993'),
(199, 'tt0751208', 3, 'Squeeze', 'MV5BMTQzMzkzNzYxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjY1Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully search for a humanoid killer whose savage murder spree reoccurs every 30 years.', 1, 3, '24 Sep. 1993'),
(200, 'tt0751094', 3, 'Conduit', 'MV5BMjM3MTg2ODU1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgzNzc3MjE@', 'Mulder becomes obsessed with solving a case that closely parallels an "encounter" he experienced as a child.', 1, 4, '1 Oct. 1993'),
(201, 'tt0751229', 3, 'The Jersey Devil', 'MV5BMTY4MTAwNzU3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA2Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully track a legendary creature that has roamed the New Jersey countryside for over 40 years.', 1, 5, '8 Oct. 1993'),
(202, 'tt0751201', 3, 'Shadows', 'MV5BMTAxMjYwMzk2OTVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDQ3NTc3NzIx', 'Mulder and Scully investigate the deaths of two men believed to have been killed by a powerful psychokinetic force.', 1, 6, '22 Oct. 1993'),
(203, 'tt0751131', 3, 'Ghost in the Machine', 'MV5BMjAxMjQ4ODA1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTE0Nzc3MjE@', 'On Halloween, Mulder and Scully investigate the death of a corporate executive who may have been murdered by a thinking computer.', 1, 7, '29 Oct. 1993'),
(204, 'tt0751141', 3, 'Ice', 'MV5BMjE2MTA4MTc2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ0Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully are sent to investigate when a team of geophysicists stationed at a remote Alaskan outpost are killed by a parasitic alien life form.', 1, 8, '5 Nov. 1993'),
(205, 'tt0751207', 3, 'Space', 'MV5BMjA5NDgxMTIzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzY1Nzc3MjE@', 'When a space shuttle mission is sabotaged, Mulder suspects it may be the work an alien spirit that inhabits the body of a former Gemini astronaut.', 1, 9, '12 Nov. 1993'),
(206, 'tt0751120', 3, 'Fallen Angel', 'MV5BMTg3MzA2MDg0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgzNzc3MjE@', 'The future of the X-Files project is jeopardized after Mulder secretly infiltrates the government cover-up of a UFO crash.', 1, 10, '19 Nov. 1993'),
(207, 'tt0751116', 3, 'Eve', 'MV5BMjA5NTE1OTk0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE0Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully search for two missing girls who disappeared after their fathers were murdered in an identical fashion.', 1, 11, '10 Dec. 1993'),
(208, 'tt0751124', 3, 'Fire', 'MV5BMzI0NzA2NDE4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzkzNzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully join forces with an inspector from Scotland Yard when a man with pyrokinetic powers stalks members of the British aristocracy.', 1, 12, '17 Dec. 1993'),
(209, 'tt0751083', 3, 'Beyond the Sea', 'MV5BMTA0NDQ0ODk3NjleQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDU2Mzc3NzIx', 'Scully believes that the pyschic predictions of a death row inmate are the only hope in apprehending a vicious murderer.', 1, 13, '7 Jan. 1994'),
(210, 'tt0751129', 3, 'Gender Bender', 'MV5BNTY5MTk5MjE4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE0Nzc3MjE@', 'A religious sect member capable of changing gender becomes the prime suspect in a murder spree.', 1, 14, '21 Jan. 1994'),
(211, 'tt0751152', 3, 'Lazarus', 'MV5BMTg3OTk1NTcwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM0Nzc3MjE@', 'The consciousness of a dangerous criminal possesses an FBI agent who is also Scully''s ex-boyfriend.', 1, 15, '4 Feb. 1994'),
(212, 'tt0751265', 3, 'Young at Heart', 'MV5BMjI1NzEwMzYxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE2Nzc3MjE@', 'A criminal believed to have died in a prison years earlier wages a vendetta against Mulder.', 1, 16, '11 Feb. 1994'),
(213, 'tt0751108', 3, 'E.B.E.', 'MV5BMTQ5MDc1NDI5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkzNzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully become the focus of a misinformation campaign when they attempt to trace the government''s secret transport of an alien life form.', 1, 17, '18 Feb. 1994'),
(214, 'tt0751162', 3, 'Miracle Man', 'MV5BMjMzOTA1OTA3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDc0Nzc3MjE@', 'The agents investigate a ministry led by a man whose son possesses the power to heal, and to kill, with a touch of his hand.', 1, 18, '18 Mar. 1994'),
(215, 'tt0751202', 3, 'Shapes', 'MV5BOTQ4NjEyMzkwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc1Nzc3MjE@', 'A creature, possibly from Native American lore, is suspected of killing a man, bringing Mulder and Scully to the Indian reservation where the attack occurred in order to uncover its identity.', 1, 19, '1 Apr. 1994'),
(216, 'tt0751097', 3, 'Darkness Falls', 'MV5BMjQwNTQ4NjIwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODEzNzc3MjE@', 'A group of loggers working in a remote forest unearths thousands of deadly insectlike creatures that paralyze and cocoon their victims.', 1, 20, '15 Apr. 1994'),
(217, 'tt0751246', 3, 'Tooms', 'MV5BMTkzODI4MjIwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk1Nzc3MjE@', 'Eugene Tooms, a supernatural killer whom Mulder helped incarcerate, is released on parole.', 1, 21, '22 Apr. 1994'),
(218, 'tt0751086', 3, 'Born Again', 'MV5BMjM0MDI5MzM5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQzNzc3MjE@', 'An 8-year-old girl is the prime suspect in a series of bizzare, seemingly unrelated deaths.', 1, 22, '29 Apr. 1994'),
(219, 'tt0751193', 3, 'Roland', 'MV5BMTcyODUwNjQzNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA1Nzc3MjE@', 'When scientists at an aeronautics lab die under mysterious circumstances, the agents suspect a mentally challenged janitor may be the culprit.', 1, 23, '6 May 1994'),
(220, 'tt0751224', 3, 'The Erlenmeyer Flask', 'MV5BNDA2OTkwMjU3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ1Nzc3MjE@', 'Deep Throat tips Mulder to a critically important case involving a missing fugitive and the cloning of extraterrestrial viruses.', 1, 24, '13 May 1994'),
(221, 'tt0751154', 3, 'Little Green Men', 'MV5BMTUwNjY2NTMxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ0Nzc3MjE@', 'With the X-Files shut down, Mulder travels to Puerto Rico, where he attempts to uncover the meaning behind the sudden termination of a communications operation.', 2, 1, '16 Sep. 1994'),
(222, 'tt0751228', 3, 'The Host', 'MV5BNzI1Njc0NjQ0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA2Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder pursues a humanoid, parasitic organism that uses sewage systems as its home.', 2, 2, '23 Sep. 1994'),
(223, 'tt0751085', 3, 'Blood', 'MV5BMTA0MzE4MTg0NDFeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDU1Mzc3NzIx', 'Mulder and Scully investigate a series of violent killings committed by seemingly normal residents of a small town.', 2, 3, '30 Sep. 1994'),
(224, 'tt0751204', 3, 'Sleepless', 'MV5BOTA0NjI1NDI5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTU1Nzc3MjE@', 'Mulder searches for a Vietnam veteran who can project his consciousness into other people''s minds.', 2, 4, '7 Oct. 1994'),
