(329, 'tt0751073', 3, 'Alpha', 'MV5BMTUxNDQzMzAzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYyNzc3MjE@', 'Mulder and Scully investigate a series of murders that may be connected to a Chinese breed of dog.', 6, 16, '28 Mar. 1999'),
(330, 'tt0751248', 3, 'Trevor', 'MV5BNDI0NzIxNTUzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk1Nzc3MjE@', 'An escaped convict apparently has the ability to pass through solid objects. He has $90,000 hidden somewhere from the bank robbery for which he was imprisoned. Mulder and Scully must find the deadly convict before he can get to his ex-girlfriend and the m', 6, 17, '11 Apr. 1999'),
(331, 'tt0751159', 3, 'Milagro', 'MV5BMjIyNjYwNTg5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTY0Nzc3MjE@', 'An introverted writer, Philip Padgett, develops an obsession with Scully and moves into Mulder''s building in order to be closer to her. Inspired by her, Padgett writes his magnum opus: a story of secret love and serial murder, featuring Scully and Padgett', 6, 18, '18 Apr. 1999'),
(332, 'tt0751239', 3, 'The Unnatural', 'MV5BMTExNDQxMDU4MzJeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDEwNjc3NzIx', 'Mulder uncovers a story involving a Negro baseball player in the 1940s who played for a minor league team in Roswell. When in a photograph he sees the Alien Bounty Hunter it is assumed that Josh Exley, the baseball player in question, might just be alien ', 6, 19, '25 Apr. 1999'),
(333, 'tt0751244', 3, 'Three of a Kind', 'MV5BMjM5Mzk0ODYzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTg1Nzc3MjE@', 'The Lone Gunmen are at a defense contractors convention in Las Vegas trying to get inside information on military secrets. When Byers spots Susanne Modeski at a casino, he convinces the other lone gunmen to trick Scully into coming to Las Vegas to help th', 6, 20, '2 May 1999'),
