(335, 'tt0419384', 3, 'Biogenesis', 'MV5BMjM2OTcyMDQyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQyMzg3MjE@', 'An artifact with strange engravings on it is found off of the coast of Africa. When a rubbing of these engravings is shown to Mulder, confusing noises happen inside his head. The agents look to uncover the origin of this mysterious artifact and to find ou', 6, 22, '16 May 1999'),
(336, 'tt0751235', 3, 'The Sixth Extinction', 'MV5BMTk4OTc0ODgwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk1Nzc3MjE@', 'In Africa, Scully searches for answers for Mulder''s condition by studying rubbings taken from the fallen spacecraft. Back in D.C., Skinner tries to help Mulder by finding Michael Kritschgau at Mulder''s request, who may know what is causing Mulder''s accele', 7, 1, '7 Nov. 1999'),
