(349, 'tt0751241', 3, 'Theef', 'MV5BMTY3NDQyNzQ4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA2Nzc3MjE@', 'Voodoo appears to be involved in the murder of a prominent doctor''s father-in-law. Mulder and Scully work to stop the killer who uses hex-craft to exact his revenge on the doctor''s family.', 7, 14, '12 Mar. 2000'),
(350, 'tt0751113', 3, 'En Ami', 'MV5BMjExMjE2NDU0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA0Nzc3MjE@', 'Agent Scully lets sympathy cloud her better judgment when she accompanies the Cigarette Smoking Man on a road trip and wonders if he''s as evil as she always thought.', 7, 15, '19 Mar. 2000'),
