(352, 'tt0751071', 3, 'All Things', 'MV5BNTA0NzgxNTczN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDEzNzc3MjE@', 'Scully is finishing up the autopsy of a person at a hospital. A file mix-up involving the autopsy folder and another patient''s x-ray leads Scully to discover a former lover of hers has been admitted at the hospital. Meeting with him again causes Scully to', 7, 17, '9 Apr. 2000'),
(353, 'tt0751087', 3, 'Brand X', 'MV5BMTYyNTA2NDM1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjUzNzc3MjE@', 'A potential witness in a high-profile tobacco case under Skinner''s supervision is found dead in his bathroom from mysterious circumstances. Skinner asks Mulder and Scully to assist him in the investigation. They find a man who smokes a unique kind of ciga', 7, 18, '16 Apr. 2000'),
(354, 'tt0751136', 3, 'Hollywood A.D.', 'MV5BNTY3NjUyMDM3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI0Nzc3MjE@', 'Skinner''s buddy from college, Wayne Federman, trails Mulder and Scully on a case involving a pipe bombing in a church, at Skinner''s insistence. Wayne is a writer/producer from Hollywood gathering material for a FBI-based movie. Mulder and Scully turn out ', 7, 19, '30 Apr. 2000'),
(355, 'tt0751123', 3, 'Fight Club', 'MV5BMTg3NDQ0MzQ5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI0Nzc3MjE@', 'Two strikingly similar women, who do not know one another, cause people to erupt into violence upon each other, whenever these two women come in contact. Mulder and Scully set out to solve the mystery of this unexplained violence involving the two women.', 7, 20, '7 May 2000'),
(356, 'tt0751145', 3, 'Je Souhaite', 'MV5BOTg3MjQxMjY5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM0Nzc3MjE@', 'Two brothers have a less than helpful genie who grants their wishes with disastrous consequences. Mulder comes into possession of the same genie, and his wishes garner similar results.', 7, 21, '14 May 2000'),
(357, 'tt0751190', 3, 'Requiem', 'MV5BMTQ0NjM0OTQxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE1Nzc3MjE@', 'Nearly a decade since their first case, Agents Mulder and Scully return to Oregon to investigate a strange entity in a forest, risking their partnership and lives.', 7, 22, '21 May 2000'),
(358, 'tt0751262', 3, 'Within', 'MV5BMjM1NTM1MjU4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI2Nzc3MjE@', 'New Deputy Director Kersh has Agent John Doggett investigate the missing Mulder case. Doggett''s skeptical treatment of Mulder''s disappearance puts a thorn in Scully and Skinner''s sides.', 8, 1, '5 Nov. 2000'),
(359, 'tt0751263', 3, 'Without', 'MV5BMTcwNjM2MzU0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE2Nzc3MjE@', 'Scully leads Skinner and an unhappy Doggett to Arizona to protect Gibson Praise from an Alien Bounty Hunter disguised as the missing Mulder.', 8, 2, '12 Nov. 2000'),
(360, 'tt0751176', 3, 'Patience', 'MV5BMTY5ODc5ODc5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTg0Nzc3MjE@', 'Scully isn''t exactly warm to Doggett on their first X-File together in which they investigate a human bat.', 8, 3, '19 Nov. 2000'),
(361, 'tt0751192', 3, 'Roadrunners', 'MV5BMjE5MTM1MTY4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE1Nzc3MjE@', 'Doggett is a little dismayed when Scully investigates a murder in a barely inhabited town in Utah without him. When Scully''s car breaks down and she finds the town people aren''t as sweet as they seem she struggles to find a way out of the demented town.', 8, 4, '26 Nov. 2000'),
(362, 'tt0751143', 3, 'Invocation', 'MV5BMTAzMTg0ODkyNzVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDEyNDc3NzIx', 'Doggett and Scully once again butt heads on their latest X-File which involves a boy who has returned after being missing for ten years but still appears to be seven years old, the age he was the day he was abducted.', 8, 5, '3 Dec. 2000'),
(363, 'tt0751186', 3, 'Redrum', 'MV5BMTgzNzU3MTc4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk0Nzc3MjE@', 'A man lives the most recent 5 days of his life backwards and finds out that he is the main suspect in the murder of his wife.', 8, 6, '10 Dec. 2000'),
