(365, 'tt0751210', 3, 'Surekill', 'MV5BMjA4MDUzNDY3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzU1Nzc3MjE@', 'Doggett and Scully deal with a killer who may have X-Ray vision.', 8, 8, '7 Jan. 2001'),
(366, 'tt0751196', 3, 'Salvage', 'MV5BMTc4NDU5MTQ2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY1Nzc3MjE@', 'A man believed to be dead from Gulf War Syndrome comes back to life and slowly turns into metal.', 8, 9, '14 Jan. 2001'),
(367, 'tt0751082', 3, 'Badlaa', 'MV5BMTk5NTIxNzY0MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEzNzc3MjE@', 'A small Indian man on a creaky cart is believed to have the ability to leap into people''s bodies.', 8, 10, '21 Jan. 2001'),
(368, 'tt0751226', 3, 'The Gift', 'MV5BNDIxOTMzMTk4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM1Nzc3MjE@', 'Skinner and Doggett investigate a case Mulder was working on before he disappeared involving a family and a monster straight from Native American lore.', 8, 11, '4 Feb. 2001'),
(369, 'tt0751157', 3, 'Medusa', 'MV5BMTU2Nzc5MzQyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY0Nzc3MjE@', 'Doggett takes to the Boston subways to try to figure out where a deadly agent that is killing citizens is coming from.', 8, 12, '11 Feb. 2001'),
(370, 'tt0751178', 3, 'Per Manum', 'MV5BMjM5MjI5NDkwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTg0Nzc3MjE@', 'Scully stumbles upon a woman whose abductee experience and symptoms are amazingly similar. The fear now is that both their upcoming births will be to non-human offspring.', 8, 13, '18 Feb. 2001'),
