(656, 'tt0664512', 9, 'Boys and Girls', 'MV5BNjE2NzE4NjA0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY4MjU1MjE@', 'Jan comes into the Scranton Branch to give all the female employees a group seminar on women in the workplace. Upset that he is not allowed in on the proceedings, Michael takes all the men of Dunder Mifflin down into the warehouse for some "guy time" with', 2, 15, '2 Feb. 2006'),
(657, 'tt0763221', 9, 'Valentine''s Day', 'MV5BNzU3MDM5OTgyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjkwODQ1MjE@', 'When Michael visits Dunder Mifflin corporate headquarters in New York on Valentine''s Day, he and Jan are both in for a surprise. Meanwhile, back in Scranton, the office staff celebrates Valentine''s Day grade school style.', 2, 16, '9 Feb. 2006'),
(658, 'tt0770626', 9, 'Dwight''s Speech', 'MV5BMzI3OTg1MTc2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI4OTU1MjE@', 'Michael coaches pompous Dwight on the finer art of public speaking after being named as Salesman of the Year.', 2, 17, '2 Mar. 2006'),
