(660, 'tt0776249', 9, 'Michael''s Birthday', 'MV5BMTQ2ODM4OTk1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQzNzU1MjE@', 'In celebration of his birthday, Michael makes a mandatory invite of the staff during the workday to go ice skating.', 2, 19, '30 Mar. 2006'),
