(662, 'tt0796140', 9, 'Conflict Resolution', 'MV5BMjM1MTk2NTkzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTgyOTQ1MjE@', 'When Michael takes over conflict resolution duties from HR, chaos ensues at Dunder Mifflin.', 2, 21, '4 May 2006'),
(663, 'tt0800604', 9, 'Casino Night', 'MV5BMjI4NjkwODkwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg5OTU1MjE@', 'The Dunder Mifflin crew holds a casino party at the warehouse and Michael has two dates.', 2, 22, '11 May 2006'),
(664, 'tt0859444', 9, 'Gay Witch Hunt', 'MV5BMTUzNjM5MDE4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ0MDU1MjE@', 'Michael apologizes to Oscar, after he finds out he''s gay, for calling him a homosexual slur--but his apology outs Oscar to the entire office. And Jim decides to take a promotion at the Stamford office.', 3, 1, '21 Sep. 2006'),
(665, 'tt0859445', 9, 'The Convention', 'MV5BMTQ4ODk1NjQxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM0MDU1MjE@', 'Micheal and Dwight go to a convention in Philadelphia and run into Jim, and Michael becomes jealous of Jim''s relationship with his new boss. Meanwhile, Pam gets ready for her first date since her engagement.', 3, 2, '28 Sep. 2006'),
