(667, 'tt0877241', 9, 'Grief Counseling', 'MV5BMTQ3NzA2OTcwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTE2ODU1MjE@', 'Michael takes on the role of office grief counselor when he learns that his old boss has died.', 3, 4, '12 Oct. 2006'),
