(669, 'tt0888293', 9, 'Diwali', 'MV5BMjIzOTMzMTEwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkyOTU1MjE@', 'Michael encourages the entire Scranton branch to support Kelly and attend a local celebration of Diwali, the Hindu Festival of Lights. Meanwhile, Andy convinces Jim to turn a late night of work into a drinking game.', 3, 6, '2 Nov. 2006'),
(670, 'tt0888292', 9, 'Branch Closing', 'MV5BMjMwMTU4NDEyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkyOTU1MjE@', 'When Jan tells Michael that the Scranton Branch will be shutting down, Michael strives to keep his staff''s spirits up. Meanwhile, everyone privately begins to envision how their lives will change in the aftermath.', 3, 7, '9 Nov. 2006'),
(671, 'tt0894520', 9, 'The Merger', 'MV5BNDY5NDE3NTkxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDA1ODU1MjE@', 'Jan informs Michael that the Scanton branch of Dunder Mifflin will be merging with the Stamford Branch. Jim and Pam are reunited while the other employees of both branches must adjust to their new co-workers.', 3, 8, '16 Nov. 2006'),
(672, 'tt0900677', 9, 'The Convict', 'MV5BMjE3NDQ3NzA2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI0NDU1MjE@', 'Michael learns that one of the new employees at Dunder Mifflin Scranton has a criminal record. Meanwhile, Jim helps Andy make a move on Pam.', 3, 9, '30 Nov. 2006'),
(673, 'tt0908674', 9, 'A Benihana Christmas', 'MV5BMTExODUwOTI5ODleQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDExNTA1NTIx', 'Trouble among the members of the party planning committee results with the office having two competing Christmas parties, but Michael isn''t interested in celebrating because he has just broken up with his girlfriend.', 3, 10, '14 Dec. 2006'),
(674, 'tt0918835', 9, 'Back from Vacation', 'MV5BMTkyMDc2Nzk0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzAxMTY1MjE@', 'Michael isn''t supposed to let anyone know that he and Jan went on vacation together in Jamaica, but he accidentally circulates a compromising photo of them to the office via e-mail.', 3, 11, '4 Jan. 2007'),
(675, 'tt0934246', 9, 'Traveling Salesmen', 'MV5BMTQyNzcwNTY0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQxNDU1MjE@', 'Dwight does a favor for Angela to keep her from getting in trouble. Andy finds out and uses it against him to get in tighter with Michael. Now Dwight must fess up, which will reveal his relationship with Angela, or risk getting fired.', 3, 12, '11 Jan. 2007'),
(676, 'tt0937879', 9, 'The Return', 'MV5BMjI4MjgyODAyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQwMjU1MjE@', 'Andy does the impossible--he makes everyone in the office miss Dwight, who is forced to take a job at Staples. Meanwhile, Oscar comes back to the office and Michael predictably throws a stereotypical Mexican party to celebrate.', 3, 13, '18 Jan. 2007'),
(677, 'tt0954759', 9, 'Ben Franklin', 'MV5BMTU1MDE0MDA3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDE3MjY1MjE@', 'Michael asks Jim to get a male stripper for Phyllis''s office bachelorette party, but he gets a Ben Franklin impersonator instead. Meanwhile, the men''s bachelor party goes as planned until Michael becomes uncomfortable with the stripper.', 3, 14, '1 Feb. 2007'),
(678, 'tt0962460', 9, 'Phyllis'' Wedding', 'MV5BMTQxNDk0NjY4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDgwOTU1MjE@', 'Michael exaggerates the importance of his small role in Phyllis''s wedding and makes an ass out of himself, and Pam notices that Phyllis stole all of her wedding ideas from her original wedding plans.', 3, 15, '8 Feb. 2007'),
(679, 'tt0964922', 9, 'Business School', 'MV5BMTQ0OTc1OTA1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDIyMjU1MjE@', 'Michael is a guest speaker for Ryan''s business class, but they have a falling-out after Michael finds out that Ryan spoke negatively about Dunder-Mifflin. And back at the office, Dwight tries to kill a bat that he found in the ceiling.', 3, 16, '15 Feb. 2007'),
(680, 'tt0967814', 9, 'Cocktails', 'MV5BMTg3NTE2MjE1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE5MzU1MjE@', 'While Michael and Jan go to their first Dunder Mifflin outing as an official couple, the office workers left behind go out for happy hour. During happy hour, Roy finds out that Jim and Pam kissed at Casino Night.', 3, 17, '22 Feb. 2007'),
(681, 'tt0983623', 9, 'The Negotiation', 'MV5BMjE2MTY5NzkxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTk5OTU1MjE@', 'Dwight saves Jim from an attack by Roy, but Dwight won''t allow Jim to thank him for it. Meanwhile, Darryl asks Michael for a pay raise, and Michael discovers that he is woefully underpaid--so Michael goes to headquarters to ask for one himself.', 3, 18, '5 Apr. 2007'),
(682, 'tt0966362', 9, 'Safety Training', 'MV5BMTk2NjAxODExOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQwMzU1MjE@', 'Andy returns to the office after weeks of anger management training, determined to make a fresh start with all the Dunder-Mifflin employees. Meanwhile, it''s safety training day in the office, and Michael and Dwight are on a mission to illuminate the dange', 3, 19, '12 Apr. 2007'),
(683, 'tt1008441', 9, 'Product Recall', 'MV5BMTAxNTEyODY5NTJeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDcyMDg0NTIx', 'Michael tries to be proactive during a watermark crisis, but only makes the situation worse. Meanwhile, Angela has trouble being apologetic with customers, and Andy discovers a secret about his new girlfriend.', 3, 20, '26 Apr. 2007'),
(684, 'tt1020711', 9, 'Women''s Appreciation', 'MV5BOTE2MzMzMDcxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzk0NzU1MjE@', 'Phyllis gets flashed in the parking lot, and Dwight goes all out to secure the premises. Michael ostensibly takes the women in the office to the mall to comfort them, but he''s really doing it to get advice about breaking up with Jan.', 3, 21, '3 May 2007'),
(685, 'tt1028389', 9, 'Beach Games', 'MV5BMjAyMDE0NjYwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzAzMDY1MjE@', 'Michael uses "beach day" at Dunder-Mifflin to find out which employee would be his most capable replacement, just in case he receives the promotion to the New York office that he''s applied for.', 3, 22, '5 May 2007'),
(686, 'tt1030253', 9, 'The Job', 'MV5BMjM1ODI5ODY2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTgzMDU1MjE@', 'Michael appoints Dwight as regional manager, anticipating that he will receive the job at corporate. Jim and Karen also interview for the same position. And Michael gets back together with Jan after she gets a boob job.', 3, 23, '17 May 2007'),
(687, 'tt1026035', 9, 'Fun Run', 'MV5BMTcyMzI2Mjc3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODkyOTU1MjE@', 'Michael accidentally runs over Meridith in the parking lot, and his guilt causes him to organize a 5-K run for her. Dwight and Angela have a falling-out after he kills her cat, and Jim and Pam''s relationship is discovered.', 4, 1, '27 Sep. 2007'),
(688, 'tt1031459', 9, 'Dunder Mifflin Infinity', 'MV5BMjEwMzE4MjU0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjM3OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael feels threatened when Ryan returns to the Scranton office to share his ideas about the future of Dunder Mifflin. Jim and Pam''s relationship is shared with the entire office, while Angela and Dwight''s relationship is on the rocks.', 4, 2, '4 Oct. 2007'),
(689, 'tt1031470', 9, 'Launch Party', 'MV5BNDM5MTA2MzEwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA3OTQ1MjE@', 'The Dunder Mifflin Infinity website is launching and Michael is excited about going to the big launch party in New York while Angela plans a satellite party for the Scranton branch. Meanwhile, Dwight competes against the website to see who can sell the mo', 4, 3, '11 Oct. 2007'),
(690, 'tt1031472', 9, 'Money', 'MV5BMTYxMDM0ODA2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjA3OTQ1MjE@', 'As Jan renovates the condo, Michael confronts his growing debt every way he can, which includes pressuring his employees for a loan. Pam and Jim spend a night out on Dwight''s family farm, now a bed and breakfast.', 4, 4, '18 Oct. 2007'),
(691, 'tt1031473', 9, 'Local Ad', 'MV5BMTk2Mjc0Njk0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDI3OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael tries to make a local Dunder Mifflin commercial that is better than the one the professional ad agency made for them. Meanwhile, Andy tries to confide in Dwight about his new relationship with Angela.', 4, 5, '25 Oct. 2007'),
(692, 'tt1031474', 9, 'Branch Wars', 'MV5BMjI4ODcwNzU1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA3OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael and Dwight try to play a prank on Karen, who is now manager of the Utica branch, after she tries to steal Stanley from the Scranton office. Meanwhile, Pam, Toby, and Oscar start their own exclusive office book club.', 4, 6, '1 Nov. 2007'),
(693, 'tt1031475', 9, 'Survivor Man', 'MV5BMTQ4MjI2ODg5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDA3OTQ1MjE@', 'After Michael isn''t invited to a camping trip with Ryan, he sets out to prove that he can brave it out in the wilderness by himself. Jim, who is in charge of the office while Michael is gone, tries to change the birthday party policy.', 4, 7, '8 Nov. 2007'),
(694, 'tt1031476', 9, 'The Deposition', 'MV5BMTA4NDc4MDA2MTVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDcwNzk0NTIx', 'Michael is put in an awkward position when Jan sues Dunder Mifflin for wrongful termination and he is deposed as a witness. Meanwhile, Kelly begins smack-talking Pam after Darryl beats Jim at Ping-Pong.', 4, 8, '15 Nov. 2007'),
(695, 'tt1031477', 9, 'Dinner Party', 'MV5BMTQyMjg1ODQwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE3OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael invites Jim and Pam and Andy and Angela to a couples-only dinner party, which makes Dwight very jealous. However, the only thing he''s missing is a ringside seat to witness Michael and Jan''s extremely dysfunctional home life.', 4, 9, '10 Apr. 2008'),
(696, 'tt1031449', 9, 'Chair Model', 'MV5BMTU4NzI1NjIyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzc1MDY2MQ@@', 'Kevin and Andy team up to reclaim the stolen Dunder Mifflin parking spaces, which forces them into a showdown with the other four bosses of the office park. Meanwhile, Michael becomes fascinated by a woman modeling chairs in a catalog.', 4, 10, '17 Apr. 2008'),
(697, 'tt1031450', 9, 'Night Out', 'MV5BMTgwNDY5NzU0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODk1MDY2MQ@@', 'Michael and Dwight go to New York to party with Ryan, who is having lots of personal and professional problems. The rest of the office employees work late, and wind up getting locked in the business park.', 4, 11, '24 Apr. 2008'),
(698, 'tt1031451', 9, 'Did I Stutter?', 'MV5BMTU2MjM3Mjc3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg2OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael tries to figure out how to respond to Stanley''s insubordination during a meeting, and Dwight buys Andy''s vehicle and immediately flips it for more money.', 4, 12, '1 May 2008'),
(699, 'tt1031452', 9, 'Job Fair', 'MV5BMTQ5MzIxNzYzNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTk2OTQ1MjE@', 'Dunder-Mifflin participates in a high school job fair, but few students are interested. Jim, Andy, and Kevin play a round of golf with a prospective client. Back at the office, everyone but Dwight and Angela leave for the day.', 4, 13, '8 May 2008'),
(700, 'tt1031453', 9, 'Goodbye, Toby', 'MV5BMjIyNjAwOTYwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTQ2OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael throws an extravagant going-away party for Toby, and falls in love with the woman who is replacing him. Jim plans to propose to Pam at the party, but gets out-staged. Back at corporate, Ryan is arrested for fraud.', 4, 14, '15 May 2008'),
(701, 'tt1236462', 9, 'Weight Loss', 'MV5BMTU0Njk5NjQ2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjcyNzU1MjE@', 'Michael tries to motivate the Scranton branch to lose weight as part of an interoffice competition. Jim is lost after Pam leaves for art school in New York, and Angela continues to see Dwight even though she is now engaged to Andy.', 5, 1, '25 Sep. 2008'),
(702, 'tt1248743', 9, 'Business Ethics', 'MV5BMjA4MjcwMDk3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkxNDU1MjE@', 'A confession at an H.R. business ethics seminar leads to a dispute between Michael and Holly over whether Meredith should be fired. Dwight tries to prove to Jim how long he can go without taking a personal break', 5, 2, '9 Oct. 2008'),
(703, 'tt1248747', 9, 'Baby Shower', 'MV5BNjk4MzQxMTMyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkxNDU1MjE@', 'After planning an office baby shower for Jan, Michael is upset when he finds out that she had the baby without him--even though he''s already been told that he''s not the baby''s father.', 5, 3, '16 Oct. 2008'),
(704, 'tt1248748', 9, 'Crime Aid', 'MV5BMTUzMTQzMjY0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael and Holly have sex for the first time, and Michael holds a fund-raiser for the office after it is burglarized. Dwight confides in Phyllis after Andy and Angela set a wedding date, and Jim runs into Pam''s ex-fiancé Roy.', 5, 4, '23 Oct. 2008'),
(705, 'tt1248749', 9, 'Employee Transfer', 'MV5BMjM1NzM1MTgzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkxNDU1MjE@', 'Holly is transferred back to New Hampshire after corporate discovers that she and Michael are dating. Dwight tries to apply to Cornell to get under Andy''s skin. Jim''s brothers and Pam decide to play a trick on Jim when they meet for lunch.', 5, 5, '30 Oct. 2008'),
(706, 'tt1248750', 9, 'Customer Survey', 'MV5BMjE5OTU1NTM4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTUxNDU1MjE@', 'Dwight and Jim believe that something is suspicious about their low customer performance ratings. After consulting with Angela, Andy finds the perfect site for their wedding--Dwight''s beet farm.', 5, 6, '6 Nov. 2008'),
(707, 'tt1248751', 9, 'Business Trip', 'MV5BMjIwNDU0ODg4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTYxNDU1MjE@', 'David Wallace sends Michael on a business trip to Winnipeg to help him forget about Holly''s transfer to Nashua, and Pam tells Jim that she failed a class and has to stay in New York City.', 5, 7, '13 Nov. 2008'),
(708, 'tt1248752', 9, 'Frame Toby', 'MV5BMTg1OTc3MzA4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTYxNDU1MjE@', 'When Michael discovers that corporate has brought back Toby to replace Holly, he tries to frame him with drugs to get him fired. Meanwhile, Jim surprises Pam by buying his parents'' house, and Pam files a secret complaint about the microwave.', 5, 8, '20 Nov. 2008'),
(709, 'tt1248753', 9, 'The Surplus', 'MV5BMjE4MTQ2MTg5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTcxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael has to spend the office surplus by they end of the day, but he can''t decide between a copier or new chairs. Dwight plays a dirty trick on Angela as they prepare for Andy and Angela''s wedding on the beet farm.', 5, 9, '4 Dec. 2008'),
(710, 'tt1248733', 9, 'Moroccan Christmas', 'MV5BMTcwMjM1MjI0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjMyNDU1MjE@', 'Phyllis blackmails Angela into doing the work for the Christmas party, which Michael turns into an intervention after Meredith gets drunk and sets her hair on fire. Meanwhile, Dwight corners the market on a popular Christmas gift.', 5, 10, '11 Dec. 2008'),
(711, 'tt1248734', 9, 'The Duel', 'MV5BNTQ3NjYzODcxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjgxNDU1MjE@', 'Moments before he leaves for New York for a meeting with David Wallace, Michael tells Andy that Angela and Dwight are seeing each other. Andy and Dwight then decide to have it out in the parking lot.', 5, 11, '15 Jan. 2009'),
(712, 'tt1248735', 9, 'Prince Family Paper', 'MV5BMjEwNTYxMzQ4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDgxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael''s conscience gets the best of him after he and Dwight go undercover to scout a family-run competitor. Back at the office, everyone else spends the day debating whether Hilary Swank is hot.', 5, 12, '22 Jan. 2009'),
(713, 'tt2340185', 10, 'Pilot', 'MV5BMTg5MzQyNjA3MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDIzNTUyMjE@', 'Billionaire playboy, Oliver Queen, has been considered dead for five years. Now, he has returned. But something, during those five years, has changed him into a mysterious green hooded archer.', 1, 1, '10 Oct. 2012'),
(714, 'tt1248736', 9, 'Stress Relief', 'MV5BNTc3NzIwMjMyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDkxNDU1MjE@', 'Dwight''s too-realistic fire alarm gives Stanley a heart attack. When he returns, Michael learns that he is the cause of Stanley''s stress. To remedy the situation, he forces the office to throw a roast for him.', 5, 13, '1 Feb. 2009'),
(715, 'tt2310910', 10, 'Honor Thy Father', 'MV5BMjE5ODA0NzI1NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE4MDYyMjE@', 'Arrow moves further along his father''s list while battling family issues with his mother, Moira, and especially with his sister. He also makes amends for past difficulties with Laurel.', 1, 2, '17 Oct. 2012'),
(716, 'tt1248737', 9, 'Lecture Circuit: Part 1', 'MV5BMTcxNTk5NjM0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgxNDU1MjE@', 'While on lecture tour to other Dunder Mifflin branches, Michael and Pam discover that Jim''s ex-girlfriend Karen is pregnant. At the office, Andy falls for a prospective client, and Jim and Dwight try to set up Kelly''s birthday party.', 5, 14, '5 Feb. 2009');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `imdb_id`, `serie_id`, `title`, `poster_id`, `summary`, `season`, `episode`, `air_date`) VALUES
(717, 'tt2310914', 10, 'Lone Gunmen', 'MV5BMjA1MjQ3OTMwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDE4MDYyMjE@', 'A mysterious sniper called Deadshot is taking out bidders at an auction for an industry company. The bidders include Oliver''s stepfather, Walter Steele.', 1, 3, '24 Oct. 2012'),
(718, 'tt1248738', 9, 'Lecture Circuit: Part 2', 'MV5BNjQ5NTAyOTg5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODgxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael and Pam go to Nashua and discover that Holly has a new boyfriend. At the office, Jim and Dwight try to come up with a theme for Kelly''s birthday party, and Angela gets a new cat.', 5, 15, '12 Feb. 2009'),
(719, 'tt2319602', 10, 'An Innocent Man', 'MV5BODgwOTE5NzY2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTQ0MjA2OA@@', 'Peter Declan has been charged with murdering his wife, and only Oliver believes he''s innocent. Arrow asks Laurel to look into Declan''s case. Meanwhile, Walter investigates a warehouse that Moira mysteriously bought with the company''s money.', 1, 4, '31 Oct. 2012'),
(720, 'tt1248739', 9, 'Blood Drive', 'MV5BMTUwOTc4OTgyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjcxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael holds a lonely hearts party on Valentine''s Day at the office, hoping that he will run into a woman he met earlier that day at a blood drive. Meanwhile, Jim and Pam have an awkward lunch with Phillis and Bob Vance.', 5, 16, '5 Mar. 2009'),
(721, 'tt2338426', 10, 'Damaged', 'MV5BMTQzOTE3Njk4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTU0MTU2OA@@', 'Oliver is accused of being the hooded archer and is put under house arrest. Also, he thinks back to his time on the island, where he first met Edward Fyers and Deathstroke.', 1, 5, '7 Nov. 2012'),
(722, 'tt1248740', 9, 'Golden Ticket', 'MV5BMzQ4MjkyNzA5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzgxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael asks Dwight to be the scapegoat for one of his business ideas that backfired badly on him. But when that idea has an unexpected positive upside, Dwight still takes credit and Michael becomes furious.', 5, 17, '12 Mar. 2009'),
(723, 'tt2377368', 10, 'Legacies', 'MV5BMTAwNzUyODMwNzdeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDA3MDY3Njg@', 'Oliver''s next target is Scott Morgan, a power executive who jacks up prices for electricity when people most need it. John Diggle suggests they go after the gang of bank robbers that recently wounded a police officer during a daytime heist. Oliver is not ', 1, 6, '14 Nov. 2012'),
(724, 'tt1248741', 9, 'New Boss', 'MV5BMjAwODA1NzU1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTgxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael gets upset when he gets a new boss to act as a buffer between him and David Wallace, and he gets even more upset when he disbands the Party Planning Committee and cancels Michael''s fifteenth anniversary party.', 5, 18, '19 Mar. 2009'),
(725, 'tt2395358', 10, 'Muse of Fire', 'MV5BMTg5NzY5NDM2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzYxOTI3OA@@', 'A new vigilante is killing off the people that work for mob boss, Frank Bertinelli.', 1, 7, '28 Nov. 2012'),
(726, 'tt1248742', 9, 'Two Weeks', 'MV5BMjEwMjUyNTczMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzkxNDU1MjE@', 'As Michael prepares to leave Dunder Mifflin, he announces that he will form his own paper company. Will anybody join him?', 5, 19, '26 Mar. 2009'),
(727, 'tt2423266', 10, 'Vendetta', 'MV5BMTk1OTE5NTU4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDc5Mjg3OA@@', 'Oliver Queen attempts to train Helena Bertinelli in the hopes that she will join him in his fight for justice. Meanwhile, Walter Steele delves deeper into his wife''s secrets.', 1, 8, '5 Dec. 2012'),
(728, 'tt1248745', 9, 'Dream Team', 'MV5BMTg4OTYwMjY3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODkxNDU1MjE@', 'Michael and Pam begin their first day as the Michael Scott Paper Company putting together the rest of the staff and trying to raise money.', 5, 20, '9 Apr. 2009'),
(729, 'tt2448164', 10, 'Year''s End', 'MV5BMTM4ODAzMDAwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDk5Mjg3OA@@', 'Oliver Queen attempts to track down a mysterious copycat vigilante who is killing people on the list.', 1, 9, '12 Dec. 2012'),
(730, 'tt1248744', 9, 'Michael Scott Paper Company', 'MV5BMjAwODM3MTg0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODg1ODc0Mg@@', 'Tension and disillusionment begin to emerge as Michael, Pam, and Ryan move the Michael Scott Paper Company into a cramped "workspace" at the business park.', 5, 21, '9 Apr. 2009'),
(731, 'tt2467064', 10, 'Burned', 'MV5BNzA2NzQwNDQ1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQyNzUyMjE@', 'Oliver''s confidence is shaken after being beaten by the Dark Archer and he takes a break from being Arrow. However, when Laurel calls Arrow for help investigating a firefighter''s suspicious death, he reluctantly agrees but his hesitance while fighting alm', 1, 10, '16 Jan. 2013'),
(732, 'tt1248746', 9, 'Heavy Competition', 'MV5BODA2NjAzMTUyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjkxNDU1MjE@', 'Dwight chooses loyalty to Dunder Mifflin over loyalty to Michael, which leads to a bitter battle between Michael and Dwight over Dwight''s accounts. Back at Dunder Mifflin, Jim pretends to confide in Andy.', 5, 22, '16 Apr. 2009'),
(733, 'tt2496078', 10, 'Trust But Verify', 'MV5BMTQyMDExODQ5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjY1MDc5OA@@', 'After a string of violent armored car robberies, Oliver suspects that Ted Gaynor of Black Hawk Security is the mastermind. His name is also on the list. It leads to a major disagreement with Digg as Gaynor was his training officer on his first tour of dut', 1, 11, '23 Jan. 2013'),
(734, 'tt1268727', 9, 'Broke', 'MV5BMTcxNzM5NjEwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ3NjU1MjE@', 'The Michael Scott Paper Company is gaining clients by offering lower prices than Dunder Mifflin, but is going broke in the process. However, Dunder Mifflin is losing clients to him, and is desperate to buy him out.', 5, 23, '23 Apr. 2009'),
(735, 'tt2519404', 10, 'Vertigo', 'MV5BMTg2MTkxMzY3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTI3NjAwOQ@@', 'Thea is about to go to trial for being under the influence but she doesn''t care because she is convinced that her mother was unfaithful to her father. Oliver tries to tell her the truth and he decides to go after who is behind the drug that she was on cal', 1, 12, '30 Jan. 2013'),
(736, 'tt1406712', 9, 'Casual Friday', 'MV5BMTYyOTA4ODkyOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjQ2NDI1Mg@@', 'Michael returns to Dunder Mifflin and brings Ryan and Pam in as salespeople, but the existing salespeople demand that Michael return the clients they stole back to them. Meanwhile, some employees take the idea of Casual Friday too far.', 5, 24, '30 Apr. 2009'),
(737, 'tt2527342', 10, 'Betrayal', 'MV5BMjM4NzM1MDEyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTIzOTUyMjE@', 'Quentin Lance''s ongoing attempt to capture the vigilante is put to a halt when a recently released criminal kidnaps his daughter to get to Arrow. Meanwhile, John Diggle insists on spying on Moira Queen to learn her secrets.', 1, 13, '6 Feb. 2013'),
(738, 'tt1417507', 9, 'Cafe Disco', 'MV5BMTYyMzAzMjMxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTI1NzU1MjE@', 'Michael tries to create a place to escape from work in the storage room that used to house the Michael Scott Paper Company, while Jim and Pam consider taking off and getting married that day.', 5, 25, '7 May 2009'),
(739, 'tt2561472', 10, 'The Odyssey', 'MV5BMTQwOTcyMzI1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzU3MDAxOQ@@', 'Oliver''s heavy-handed approach to getting information from his mother backfires and she manages to shoot him in the shoulder. He turns to Felicity Smoak for help getting back to his hideaway. She and Digg do their best to nurse him back to health. Flashba', 1, 14, '13 Feb. 2013'),
(740, 'tt1417732', 9, 'Company Picnic', 'MV5BMTMwMTMyNDg2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTI4MTY1Mg@@', 'Michael runs into Holly at the company picnic, and the two of them accidentally reveal that the Buffalo branch is closing during a comedy skit before corporate has made the announcement.', 5, 26, '14 May 2009'),
(741, 'tt2605292', 10, 'Dodger', 'MV5BMTQ5NzY3ODcwMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDQ3MDAxOQ@@', 'A jewel thief known as the Dodger who coerces people to steal for him by strapping an explosive to them, is in town. So Oliver decides to use his family''s jewels as bait to lure him. But he chooses someone close to Oliver to plant the explosive. Thea''s pu', 1, 15, '20 Feb. 2013'),
(742, 'tt1467798', 9, 'Gossip', 'MV5BNTMwNzEzNDU2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDUyODQ1MjE@', 'Michael regrets revealing that Stanley is having an affair, so he spreads a bunch of lies about everyone else to cover his tracks--except that one of the lies that he spread actually turns out to be true.', 6, 1, '17 Sep. 2009'),
(743, 'tt2633630', 10, 'Dead to Rights', 'MV5BODcxMTQ1MDY0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzIxOTYxOQ@@', 'The plan to kill Malcolm Merlyn goes into operation. Arrow kills one assassin who has just arrived in the city and retrieves his cellphone. It''s up to Felicity to break into it and find out just who the target is. A birthday dinner for Tommy Merlyn is int', 1, 16, '27 Feb. 2013'),
(744, 'tt1487740', 9, 'The Meeting', 'MV5BMTU3MjAwMzI0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjU3OTM4Mg@@', 'Michael sabotages--then promotes--Jim''s efforts at getting a promotion, while Dwight and Toby try to prove that Darryl has submitted a fraudulent medical claim.', 6, 2, '24 Sep. 2009'),
(745, 'tt2654070', 10, 'The Huntress Returns', 'MV5BMTc3NDU4NTQ0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDkxNDQyOQ@@', 'Helena is back to seek vengeance, but Oliver still has feeling toward her. The Arrow must stop and kill her, but at what costs? Now that several of his closest friends know about his true identity, no one is safe.', 1, 17, '20 Mar. 2013'),
(746, 'tt1487741', 9, 'The Promotion', 'MV5BMTg4ODEyMDkzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAyNzU1MjE@', 'Jim discovers just how hard being the boss can be when David Wallace forces Michael and him to determine which employees will be getting a raise.', 6, 3, '1 Oct. 2009'),
(747, 'tt2698256', 10, 'Salvation', 'MV5BNDU4NjgxNzk4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTgxNDQyOQ@@', 'After a major fire, Oliver decides it''s time to eliminate real estate developer and slumlord John Nicol, another person on his father''s list. He''s beaten to the punch when another vigilante, The Savior, who kidnaps Nicol and ultimately executes him - broa', 1, 18, '27 Mar. 2013'),
(748, 'tt1487742', 9, 'Niagara', 'MV5BMTQ4MDQwNDA0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTcxNzU1MjE@', 'The Office travels to Niagara Falls to celebrate Jim and Pam''s wedding under strict orders not to mention Pam''s pregnancy. Michael, Dwight, and Andy all want to hook up with guests at the wedding and Michael and Dwight meet twins.', 6, 4, '8 Oct. 2009'),
(749, 'tt2712930', 10, 'Unfinished Business', 'MV5BMTEwNTc1MDEzNTheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDkwMDk5Mjk@', 'Vertigo is again appearing on the market even though The Count, who created the drug, is still in a psychiatric hospital. Soon after Oliver confirms that he''s still there, he somehow manages to escape. The Count''s psychiatrist says his patient overpowered', 1, 19, '3 Apr. 2013'),
(750, 'tt1520196', 9, 'Mafia', 'MV5BMTQ2Njk4NDgxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQzNjU1MjE@', 'Michael meets with an insurance salesman that visits the office and is later convinced by Dwight and Andy that he is part of the mafia. Erin accidentally ruins Pam''s painting.', 6, 5, '15 Oct. 2009'),
(751, 'tt2761432', 10, 'Home Invasion', 'MV5BMTcyMzY3NTI5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTE5NDI0OQ@@', 'Oliver decides that his next target is going to be someone on Digg''s list: Deadshot. They set a trap for him and Digg''s spy friends get involved as well. Meanwhile, Laurel''s latest clients are Eric and Nancy Moore who have agreed to testify against Edward', 1, 20, '24 Apr. 2013'),
(752, 'tt1520197', 9, 'The Lover', 'MV5BMTQ2OTU1NjQzNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzUzNjU1MjE@', 'Jim and Pam return from their honeymoon and learn, to their horror, that Michael is dating Pam''s mom. Meanwhile, Dwight gives Jim a "gift"--which actually has a listening device attached to it.', 6, 6, '22 Oct. 2009'),
(753, 'tt2761428', 10, 'The Undertaking', 'MV5BMzQxMjk0ODcyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDc0MzU0OQ@@', 'After taking a mob accountant''s laptop, Oliver plans to return the money to its rightful owners. Felicity however finds that Dominic Alonzo - the operator of an illegal casino and the head of a gang known for kidnapping - was paid $2 million to kidnap Wal', 1, 21, '1 May 2013'),
(754, 'tt1524878', 9, 'Koi Pond', 'MV5BMjAzMDQ3MzQ2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI2NDU1MjE@', 'Michael is upset when he becomes the butt of all the office jokes after he falls in a koi pond. Andy and Pam go out together on some cold calls, and everybody mistakes them as a married couple.', 6, 7, '29 Oct. 2009'),
(755, 'tt2761434', 10, 'Darkness on the Edge of Town', 'MV5BMzAxNzU5OTA1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjU0MzU0OQ@@', 'The time is fast approaching for the Undertaking to occur and Malcolm Merlyn begins to tidy up the loose ends, beginning with the scientists at UNIDAC. Oliver and Digg trick Moira into telling just what the Undertaking is about. Oliver realizes that even ', 1, 22, '8 May 2013'),
(756, 'tt1531589', 9, 'Double Date', 'MV5BMjIzNzI3NTkyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTg3OTQ1MjE@', 'Michael sparks more anger from Pam when he breaks up with her mom on her birthday after he finds out she''s 58, and Dwight unsuccessfully tries to get everyone in the office to owe him a favor.', 6, 8, '5 Nov. 2009'),
(757, 'tt2761440', 10, 'Sacrifice', 'MV5BMTk4MzUyMjEzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzAyMDg0OQ@@', 'Oliver awakens to find himself Malcolm Merlyn''s prisoner. He manages to escape and away with help from Digg. Malcolm accelerates his timetable as a result. Felicity is questioned by Det. Lance about her hacking activities but is interrupted by Oliver who ', 1, 23, '15 May 2013'),
(758, 'tt1535367', 9, 'Murder', 'MV5BMTQ2NDg4MDA2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQxOTQ1MjE@', 'The entire office is preoccupied about rumors of Dunder Mifflin''s bankruptcy. Michael tries to create a distraction by engaging everyone in murder-mystery game, but Jim wonders if that is a good idea.', 6, 9, '12 Nov. 2009'),
(759, 'tt2702698', 10, 'City of Heroes', 'MV5BMTUxODEwMzU5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODYwMTczMDE@', 'Diggle and Felicity return to island to convince Oliver to return as the Arrow.', 2, 1, '9 Oct. 2013'),
(760, 'tt1536326', 9, 'Shareholder Meeting', 'MV5BMTUxNTgzNzQ4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjE2NzQ1MjE@', 'Michael speaks out of line at the Dunder Mifflin shareholders meeting and creates a big problem for management, while Jim discovers that nobody in the office thinks he''s the "real" boss.', 6, 10, '19 Nov. 2009'),
