(996, 'tt4806004', 13, 'The Fury of Firestorm', 'MV5BMjA5ODk0Nzc4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTY5MTgxNzE@', 'Barry and the team look for another Firestorm match for Dr. Stein. When the team meets Jefferson Jackson, Caitlin has her reservations about whether Jax is the right match for Dr. Stein. Iris surprises Joe while Barry and Patty grow closer.', 2, 4, '27 Oct. 2015'),
(997, 'tt4818206', 13, 'The Darkness and the Light', 'MV5BMTQ3NjU4MTk5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEwMjgxNzE@', 'Barry learns a new breacher, Dr. Light, has come through the portal and sets off to capture her. Jay tells Barry that Dr. Light was not a threat on Earth-2 and that Barry can reason with her. However, during a fight with The Flash, she blinds him and drop', 2, 5, '3 Nov. 2015'),
(998, 'tt4838244', 13, 'Enter Zoom', 'MV5BMjA1MjMwNjM4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkxMTMyNzE@', 'Barry and his team plan to trap Zoom with Linda''s help while Joe is against it.', 2, 6, '10 Nov. 2015'),
(999, 'tt4848704', 13, 'Gorilla Warfare', 'MV5BMTg3Njg0Mzc1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ5NzUyNzE@', 'Barry races to rescue Caitlyn when Grodd kidnaps her; Cisco plans a date with the new barista at Jitters; Patty thinks Barry is hiding something.', 2, 7, '17 Nov. 2015'),
(1000, 'tt4857182', 13, 'Legends of Today', 'MV5BMjEyNjc1MDY4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzUyOTMzNzE@', 'When Vandal Savage attacks Kendra Saunders, Barry takes Kendra to Starling City, seeking Oliver''s protection; Harrison asks Jay to test a new serum to make Barry run faster.', 2, 8, '1 Dec. 2015'),
(1001, 'tt4859306', 13, 'Running to Stand Still', 'MV5BMzY0OTY0OTg3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTMyNjQ0NzE@', 'Weather Wizard returns to break Captain Cold and The Trickster out of Iron Heights, but Barry is determined to not let that happen. Meanwhile, Joe and Iris meet Wally West. Harrison Wells accepts to work with Zoom against Barry.', 2, 9, '8 Dec. 2015'),
(1002, 'tt4859308', 13, 'Potential Energy', 'MV5BMjMxNTAyMzE3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzg2NDc3NzE@', 'Barry and the Star Labs team hunt down The Turtle who can slow down time especially anyone with speed. Barry faces a choice on whether or not Patty should learn his secret identity especially after Zoom returns to Earth 1 to kidnap her.', 2, 10, '19 Jan. 2016'),
(1003, 'tt4899778', 13, 'The Reverse-Flash Returns', 'MV5BMTA4MTExNzIxNDheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDg4NzgxODcx', 'Dr Harrison figures out how to induce Cisco''s ability They hence learn that Eobard Thawne is still alive. Iris is saying farewell to her mother. Patty realizes there''s more to Barry than meets the eye.', 2, 11, '26 Jan. 2016'),
(1004, 'tt5017986', 13, 'Fast Lane', 'MV5BMTk3MDY3MTMyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODczMjk4NzE@', 'Barry and Wells team up to figure out a way to close the breaches but their plan has stalled because of a new meta human named Tar-Pit. Iris is concerned for Wally''s safety after she finds out he is involved in drag racing. After he refuses to stop she ma', 2, 12, '2 Feb. 2016'),
(1005, 'tt5028206', 13, 'Welcome to Earth-2', '01', 'Barry, Wells and Cisco travels to Earth-2 to rescue Jesse from Zoom. He finds killer Frost and Deathstorm whom are Caitlin and Ronnie on Earth-1 While Jay took barry''s responibility on defending central city from a meta human called Geomancer.', 2, 13, '9 Feb. 2016'),
