(1359, 'tt2825694', 15, 'Double Blind', 'MV5BMTM3ODU5NTEzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTM5Nzc0OQ@@', 'A Navy petty officer chases and attacks a man; he asks to speak with someone at NCIS; the gang solve. An official from the DoD starts snooping around, apparently on a witch hunt; he and a goon squad of grim feds confront Gibbs. [Continued.]', 10, 23, '7 May 2013'),
(1360, 'tt2841580', 15, 'Damned If You Do', 'MV5BNzAyNTQwNzY0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTM5Nzc0OQ@@', 'A familiar face defends Gibbs in Parson''s investigation. While the team tries to help Gibbs, they must solve the murder of a Navy SEAL.', 10, 24, '14 May 2013'),
(1361, 'tt2961332', 15, 'Whiskey Tango Foxtrot', 'MV5BMjA3NjA3MzgzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTk2NzgxMDE@', 'Parsons gripes about his project; then a bomb explodes, killing the SecNav; Gibbs volunteers for a spec op, which takes him to Iran, where he runs into Parsons, and where they investigate. Tony tries to pursue Ziva in Israel. [Continued.]', 11, 1, '24 Sep. 2013'),
(1362, 'tt3106866', 15, 'Past, Present, and Future', 'MV5BMTcyMzY5MzYwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ2MjUzMDE@', 'Tony searches for Ziva in Israel and elsewhere; he finally finds her, but he returns without her. Gibbs, Fornell, and others work hard on the case of the bomber. McGee makes a huge discovery, which allows Gibbs to solve and to take a shot.', 11, 2, '1 Oct. 2013'),
(1363, 'tt3118320', 15, 'Under the Radar', 'MV5BMTQxMTc3MjE2M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzc1Nzg0MjE@', 'A bomb explodes inside the unoccupied pad of a Navy jaygee; Gibbs and company investigate; Abby determines who built the bomb; Tony finds the seller of the explosive; the team find the jaygee, who changes his plan and ends his flight.', 11, 3, '8 Oct. 2013'),
(1364, 'tt3166472', 15, 'Anonymous Was a Woman', 'MV5BMjMwOTUxNjg5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzA5Mjg0MjE@', 'Gibbs and company investigate the death of a woman with an ID card of a sergeant in the US Marine Corps; McGee finds that the real sergeant died in Afghanistan three years ago. Gibbs and McGee go to Kabul, sort things out, and do some good.', 11, 4, '15 Oct. 2013'),
(1365, 'tt3219082', 15, 'Once a Crook', 'MV5BMTcyOTIzOTg4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTU3NTc0MDE@', 'A Navy petty officer dies of a gunshot in a park in Baltimore, Maryland; Gibbs and company investigate; at the scene Tony sees a clue and a man. Abby finds links, then the gang put the pieces together and nail the shooter. Tony nods off.', 11, 5, '22 Oct. 2013'),
(1366, 'tt3219088', 15, 'Oil and Water', 'MV5BODE0NjU2NDk5MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzg2NTc0MDE@', 'An explosion and a fire damage an offshore drilling platform near the Virginia Capes, killing one (a major in the US Marine Corps Reserve) and injuring many others; Gibbs and company, along with Abby of the CGIS, investigate. The CEO and the chief legal c', 11, 6, '29 Oct. 2013'),
(1367, 'tt3219092', 15, 'Better Angels', 'MV5BNjA5NzczMzgzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ1NTU1MDE@', 'A Marine sergeant, Dawson, dies of gunfire during an alleged armed robbery of a men''s clothing store in Washington, DC; Gibbs and company investigate; while at the scene Gibbs receives a call from a local cop nearby in Howard County, Maryland, near Baltim', 11, 7, '5 Nov. 2013'),
(1368, 'tt3268312', 15, 'Alibi', 'MV5BMTUwODQ3NTU0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzcwMDA2MDE@', 'At night at Quantico a hit-and-run driver kills a woman Navy petty officer; while investigating, Gibbs and company find a suspect, who has a solid but complicated alibi; the gang, a lawyer, and a local cop figure out the whole thing.', 11, 8, '12 Nov. 2013'),
(1369, 'tt3268322', 15, 'Gut Check', 'MV5BODc3MjY5OTk4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk2OTQ2MDE@', 'A security system detects a bug on the person of the SecNav; Tony contacts the NSA, where he finds a two-year-old paper describing such a breach; one man dies; the author helps the gang to nail the bad guys; Gibbs wants to keep her around.', 11, 9, '19 Nov. 2013'),
(1370, 'tt3297782', 15, 'Devil''s Triad', 'MV5BMTAxNzEzNDAxNTBeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDUwMTk2NzAx', 'A clown kills a Marine corporal; while investigating, Gibbs and company find Fornell, Diane, and her boyfriend, who says that he''s someone else, and that he knows the clown. All the pieces come together, and the team bust the main bad guy.', 11, 10, '10 Dec. 2013'),
(1371, 'tt3314594', 15, 'Homesick', 'MV5BMTY2MzI2ODQ2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzc4ODA4MDE@', 'Within 30 miles of Washington, DC, eight kids in Navy and Marine Corps families have suddenly become badly ill, requiring treatment in ERs and ICUs; Gibbs and company investigate; Carol, of the Naval Medical-research Center, joins the effort; immediately ', 11, 11, '17 Dec. 2013'),
(1372, 'tt3336374', 15, 'Kill Chain', 'MV5BNjg4Mzg1MzAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY1MTg0MjE@', 'A Navy petty officer dies of gunfire in a park in Washington, DC; Gibbs and company investigate; Hollis helps. The gang find an accessory for hire to a terrorist. An explosion kills six and injures 22, including Delilah. [Continued.]', 11, 12, '7 Jan. 2014'),
(1373, 'tt3315394', 15, 'Double Back', 'MV5BMTQ3NjEwMTg4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQ0MzY5MDE@', 'While McGee stays with Delilah in a hospital, Gibbs, Tony, and Ellie find and recover a bullet, which bears the DNA of the wheelman, whom Gibbs clipped during the escape; Abby identifies him, and she and Tony gather data about him, which Gibbs and Duck re', 11, 13, '14 Jan. 2014'),
(1374, 'tt3441178', 15, 'Monsters and Men', 'MV5BMjIxOTUwOTY5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODUzOTYwMTE@', 'Ellie''s gut says that Parsa is in his home district in NW Pakistan; there a SEAL team captures him alive. Gibbs, McGee, and Ellie fly to an aircraft carrier, where Gibbs and Ellie question him. Ellie gets into a bind, but Gibbs saves her.', 11, 14, '4 Feb. 2014'),
(1375, 'tt3462648', 15, 'Bulletproof', 'MV5BMTU0MDMzNDc5NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDU2NDYyMTE@', 'An overturned van in Washington, DC, contains body armor, which Abby shows to be faulty and fatal; Gibbs and company find the body of the driver, then the source of the bad gear and the path to the troops in the Middle East. Justice wins.', 11, 15, '25 Feb. 2014'),
(1376, 'tt3548330', 15, 'Dressed to Kill', 'MV5BMjI2MzIyOTU4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY2NDYyMTE@', 'When Tony seeks to question a man who appears to impersonate a Naval officer, the man draws a pistol; Tony kills him. The dead man proves to be a private investigator who had become involved in international intrigue. The gang sort it out.', 11, 16, '4 Mar. 2014'),
(1377, 'tt3548334', 15, 'Rock and a Hard Place', 'MV5BMTU1ODY4MjA2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjIzMTA0MTE@', 'Backstage before a charity-benefit concert in Washington, DC, an explosion kills a Navy petty officer first-class; Gibbs and company investigate; Abby fingers the bad guy, McGee finds out about him, and Gibbs and Ellie catch him at work.', 11, 17, '18 Mar. 2014'),
(1378, 'tt3548332', 15, 'Crescent City: Part 1', 'MV5BMTQyNTg0MDY3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk5MTY0MTE@', 'In New Orleans, Louisiana, two local special agents of the NCIS, Pride and LaSalle, start to investigate the death of Dan McLane, who was not only a member of the US House of Representatives but also both a retired Naval Reserve commander and a retired ag', 11, 18, '25 Mar. 2014'),
(1379, 'tt3548338', 15, 'Crescent City: Part 2', 'MV5BMTQ4NDkzMTUzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMwMjY0MTE@', 'While investigating the death of a US congressman, the Gibbs team and the gang in Nola continue to seek both a killer and a connection to an old case. Another man dies. Ducky suggests a theory, and the bunch put all the pieces together.', 11, 19, '1 Apr. 2014'),
(1380, 'tt3624172', 15, 'Page Not Found', 'MV5BMTYwMTM2ODEwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk0Mzk0MTE@', 'Delilah finds a clue, which may help to solve the alleged death of a US Navy lieutenant, Kit, two weeks ago in Budapest, Hungary; then her boss orders her that she has never seen it; however, she surreptitiously speaks with Tony, McGee, and Gibbs, who sen', 11, 20, '8 Apr. 2014'),
(1381, 'tt3645016', 15, 'Alleged', 'MV5BNzMxMTA2MTIxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjE1MTA2MTE@', 'A distracted texting driver runs over the dead body of a Naval officer; Gibbs and company investigate; they find a connection to a previously unreported rape of a drugged victim. The team figure out everything, and they catch the bad guy.', 11, 21, '15 Apr. 2014'),
(1382, 'tt3648356', 15, 'Shooter', 'MV5BMTQzNDIyNDcyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDE1MTA2MTE@', 'During a court-martial of an Army first lieutenant, a Marine photojournalist disappears before he can testify; while Gibbs and company lend a hand, they find the body of the Marine, solve his murder and another one, and arrest two bad guys.', 11, 22, '29 Apr. 2014'),
(1383, 'tt3688136', 15, 'The Admiral''s Daughter', 'MV5BMjA1Mzg4MzYwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE0Mjk2MTE@', 'Tony goes to France to escort an admiral''s daughter, Amanda, back to DC; meanwhile Gibbs and company investigate a death. Tony and Amanda run into trouble, work it out, find solutions for all seven executions, and report to the admiral.', 11, 23, '6 May 2014'),
(1384, 'tt3693236', 15, 'Honor Thy Father', 'MV5BMjAwNzQ4NjYyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY2OTg3MTE@', 'The team must investigate a prison escape without Gibbs as he heads to Stillwater after his father''s death.', 11, 24, '13 May 2014'),
(1385, 'tt3607318', 15, 'Twenty Klicks', 'MV5BNzE4NDI5OTQxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzI2OTM3MjE@', 'Gibbs and McGee are shot down in a Naval helicopter over remote parts of Russia while on a mission to escort an NCIS computer geek safely home. Meanwhile, the gang at home anxiously work to help bring them all home safely.', 12, 1, '23 Sep. 2014'),
(1386, 'tt4012522', 15, 'Kill the Messenger', 'MV5BMjE2MzUxNzUyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU0NDE4MjE@', 'A Navy Commander is murdered near the White House, it is learned that he was on his way to talk to the President. Gibbs and his team must determine if it is because of his relationship with the President or because of his marital problems.', 12, 2, '30 Sep. 2014'),
(1387, 'tt4012538', 15, 'So It Goes', 'MV5BMTYwNjMwODYxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDg0NDE4MjE@', 'Flashbacks into his past help tell the tale for Dr. Mallard as he and Bishop travel to England in search of answers to find out why an Englishman murdered in the United States would have a list of deceased Navy men on his person.', 12, 3, '7 Oct. 2014'),
(1388, 'tt4012552', 15, 'Choke Hold', 'MV5BMTU1ODE5ODg4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODQ2NTIwMzE@', 'After a scientist is decapitated by a strangulation device in a park, Gibbs and his team search for the woman who was her former research partner in Russia in order to learn who is behind her murder. They learn it may be a familiar foe.', 12, 4, '14 Oct. 2014'),
(1389, 'tt4054082', 15, 'The San Dominick', 'MV5BMTUxMzUyNTg4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDY4NzY5MjE@', 'While the NCIS team is on a training exercise with CGIS Special Agent Abigail Borin, Gibbs spots a man overboard. It leads him to board another ship called The San Dominick, and he soon discovers that it has been taken over by pirates.', 12, 5, '21 Oct. 2014');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `imdb_id`, `serie_id`, `title`, `poster_id`, `summary`, `season`, `episode`, `air_date`) VALUES
(1390, 'tt4043144', 15, 'Parental Guidance Suggested', 'MV5BMTkwNDc2MDU3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjk2NzEwMzE@', 'The wife of a Navy Seal is murdered, and the NCIS team discovers she has a background in criminal forensics and recently visited a serial killer in prison seeking his help with another sociopath. Gibbs and company must figure out who it is.', 12, 6, '28 Oct. 2014'),
(1391, 'tt4054094', 15, 'The Searchers', 'MV5BMTc4MzU3NjY4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODc0NTA0MzE@', 'While investigating the death of a retired Marine Master Sergeant, Gibbs and the NCIS team discover there is a possibility that his death may be connected to another Marine who was MIA from the Vietnam War.', 12, 7, '11 Nov. 2014'),
(1392, 'tt4115942', 15, 'Semper Fortis', 'MV5BMjMzNjk4NjQzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjg0NTA0MzE@', 'A former Navy hospital corpsman gives aid to the victims of a wreck; local officials arrest her for practicing medicine without a license; Gibbs and company find the other driver, his killer, and a lawyer who makes a deal for the corpsman.', 12, 8, '18 Nov. 2014'),
(1393, 'tt4137658', 15, 'Grounded', 'MV5BMTQxODQxNTUxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTcwODQ0MzE@', 'On the eve of Thanksgiving, DiNozzo and Bishop experience a weather delay at the D.C airport when Gibbs informs them of an elevated terror threat specific to area airports. An impostor posing as an air marshal leads them to the real threat.', 12, 9, '25 Nov. 2014'),
(1394, 'tt4238980', 15, 'House Rules', 'MV5BOTE4NDYzMTU0NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA3NDE3MzE@', 'Tis the season to be hacking. In a Christmas letter to his father, McGee describes in detail a case in which he, Gibbs and the rest of the NCIS team investigate the hackers who are responsible for the Internet going down in the D.C. area.', 12, 10, '16 Dec. 2014'),
(1395, 'tt4290812', 15, 'Check', 'MV5BNjM0NjY4MDEzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTA1NjI5MzE@', 'The NCIS team investigate a series of crime scenes that appear to be copycats of previous cases. Meanwhile, two of Gibbs'' ex-wives show up at a crime scene to discuss something important with him.', 12, 11, '6 Jan. 2015'),
(1396, 'tt4329538', 15, 'The Enemy Within', 'MV5BMTg2NjAwNzQ2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQzMjU5NDE@', 'Gibbs and the rest of the NCIS team, along with FBI agent Fornell are on the hunt for an American born terrorist who was detected in Syria but is now back in the D.C area.', 12, 12, '13 Jan. 2015'),
(1397, 'tt4382126', 15, 'We Build, We Fight', 'MV5BMTg1MDAxOTU0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ2OTMzNDE@', 'When an openly-gay Navy Lieutenant who was about to be awarded the Medal of Honor is murdered, Gibbs and the team investigate. Meanwhile, Breena goes into labor.', 12, 13, '3 Feb. 2015'),
(1398, 'tt4410500', 15, 'Cadence', 'MV5BMTQ1MjQwNDkzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY4MTI0NDE@', 'DiNozzo returns to the military academy he attended as a teenager after a murdered Marine and alumni of the school is found clutching the photo of a current student. Also, Bishop and her husband invite Gibbs and the team out for a special dinner.', 12, 14, '10 Feb. 2015'),
(1399, 'tt4426784', 15, 'Cabin Fever', 'MV5BOTk1MTYxNDQ4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTc1NTA1NDE@', 'Gibbs and the NCIS team continue to track down the Russian terrorist Sergei after two young Marines are killed in a bombing. Agent Fornell struggles to cope with the recent shooting death of his ex-wife at the hands of Sergei.', 12, 15, '17 Feb. 2015'),
(1400, 'tt4468870', 15, 'Blast from the Past', 'MV5BMTYxODUyMTU0Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTcwNjU4NDE@', 'A covert identity created for one of Gibbs'' undercover cases 20 years ago resurfaces after a murder victim is found living under the alias.', 12, 16, '24 Feb. 2015'),
(1401, 'tt4483286', 15, 'The Artful Dodger', 'MV5BMjM1NTg1MjAwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk3MjQ3NDE@', 'After a Vice Admirals aide is murdered, Gibbs and the NCIS team theorize that it was because of a valuable painting in her office. DiNozzo''s father is more than happy to help with the investigation by sharing his knowledge of the artwork.', 12, 17, '10 Mar. 2015'),
(1402, 'tt4520076', 15, 'Status Update', 'MV5BMjM1NzkzMDg4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU3ODEwNTE@', 'After the body of a thief is found in a Marine''s house, NCIS discovers the calling card of a terror group Delilah and the Department of Defense have been tracking. Margo Harshman guest stars.', 12, 18, '24 Mar. 2015'),
(1403, 'tt4536378', 15, 'Patience', 'MV5BMzQzODY4MDg0N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY3NDcyNTE@', 'A petty officer''s murder provides clues to a 40 year unsolved airport bombing which Gibbs and DiNozzo have been reexamining recently.', 12, 19, '31 Mar. 2015'),
(1404, 'tt4573232', 15, 'No Good Deed', 'MV5BMTQ2Njc4OTgyMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODk2MzUyNTE@', 'DiNozzo is partnered with his girlfriend, ATF Special Agent Zoë Keates, after evidence reveals that the murder weapon in an NCIS case was originally purchased for the controversial ATF sting, "Operation Fast and Furious." Also, Anthony DiNozzo Sr. returns', 12, 20, '7 Apr. 2015'),
(1405, 'tt4573234', 15, 'Lost in Translation', 'MV5BMzQ3ODkzOTA1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDU3MjQzNTE@', 'Gibbs and Bishop travel to Afghanistan when a murder investigation is linked to a terror group holding a Marine hostage. Meanwhile, Tony is annoyed when McGee steals his gig as the face of the NCIS recruitment brochures.', 12, 21, '14 Apr. 2015'),
(1406, 'tt4573238', 15, 'Troll', 'MV5BODgzNzQ0OTI3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkwOTQ1NTE@', 'Special Agent Ned Dorneget from NCIS cyber operations assists the team when a Navy ensign who worked in the Office of Naval Intelligence is murdered. Also, the team discovers that Jake and Gibbs have become good friends.', 12, 22, '28 Apr. 2015'),
(1407, 'tt4573240', 15, 'The Lost Boys', 'MV5BMTc5NDE0NjI1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYzMzI2NTE@', 'The NCIS cyber case turns into a united global effort after evidence confirms "The Calling," an international terrorist group that recruits children through the Internet, has been purchasing German S-mines off the black market.', 12, 23, '5 May 2015'),
(1408, 'tt4573242', 15, 'Neverland', 'MV5BNTYyMjYwODA2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDc2NTI3NTE@', 'NCIS feverishly investigates a global terrorist group that is recruiting teens via the Internet, following a deadly bombing overseas that results in an emotional and surprising loss for the team.', 12, 24, '12 May 2015'),
(1409, 'tt4938932', 15, 'Stop the Bleeding', 'MV5BODA4NjM2OTIzM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzc1MTg4NjE@', 'Gibbs fights for his life after being shot by Luke Harris. Meanwhile, Agent Tony DiNozzo and CIA officer Joanna Teague travel to Egypt to take down The Calling.', 13, 1, '22 Sep. 2015'),
(1410, 'tt5052284', 15, 'Personal Day', 'MV5BMTU2NjY0MDA2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjA4ODM5NjE@', 'Gibbs asks the team to work on a case with a DEA Agent to bring down a drug dealer who is connected to the Gibbs and the agent.', 13, 2, '29 Sep. 2015'),
(1411, 'tt5053312', 15, 'Incognito', 'MV5BMTczMDAzNzY4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk4OTg5NjE@', 'Hours after calling Gibbs about a possible case, a Marine is found dead in Quantico; McGee and Bishop pose as a married couple.', 13, 3, '6 Oct. 2015'),
(1412, 'tt5087808', 15, 'Double Trouble', 'MV5BNzI5MjE4MjA5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzc2NTQwNzE@', 'Vance partners with Gibbs and returns to field duty when a murder case is connected to a former NCIS agent he put in jail for stealing evidence.', 13, 4, '13 Oct. 2015'),
(1413, 'tt5009596', 15, 'Lockdown', 'MV5BNDA2MzY1NzM0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkxMDAxNzE@', 'During an investigation, Abby is trapped in a pharmaceutical lab when armed men enter the building and take hostages.', 13, 5, '20 Oct. 2015'),
(1414, 'tt5115180', 15, 'Viral', 'MV5BMTUzNDcxMzUzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzA3NTkxNzE@', 'When a petty officer is murdered, the crime matches a local serial killer''s method of operation; Delilah and McGee prepare to move in together.', 13, 6, '27 Oct. 2015'),
(1415, 'tt5105524', 15, '16 Years', 'MV5BMjQxMjMxNzUyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIwNDAyNzE@', 'NCIS investigates the death of a retired Navy officer who''s son was convicted of a murder 16 years before. A flawed forensic test from that time can prove whether the son was the real murderer or innocent of the crime.', 13, 7, '3 Nov. 2015'),
(1416, 'tt5160036', 15, 'Saviors', 'MV5BMTQ5NzE3ODM3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjc5MjUyNzE@', 'DiNozzo is reunited with his ex-girlfriend, Jeanne Benoit, when insurgents in Sudan attack a group of volunteer doctors, including her husband. DiNozzo and McGee travel to the crime scene for the joint murder and kidnapping case and join the search for th', 13, 8, '10 Nov. 2015'),
(1417, 'tt5197818', 15, 'Day in Court', 'MV5BMjc2MzUxMTExNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODAzMjAzNzE@', 'A Petty Officer, accused of killing an ex-girlfriend, is set free on mistrial. Professing to be innocent he asks NCIS to investigate and if necessary court martial him. Bishop and her husband have marital problems.', 13, 9, '17 Nov. 2015'),
(1418, 'tt5153336', 15, 'Blood Brothers', 'MV5BMTQ3NzkxMzc1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY0ODQzNzE@', 'The Secretary of Defense turns to NCIS to help a sailor dying from leukemia locate a bone marrow transplant after two of his siblings are killed in the line of duty. Meanwhile, Bishop returns home to Oklahoma for Thanksgiving after learning of Jake''s chea', 13, 10, '24 Nov. 2015'),
(1419, 'tt5245386', 15, 'Spinning Wheel', 'MV5BMTk0NDE3MTk4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDcxMzA1NzE@', 'After Ducky is attacked by a man claiming to have information about his half-brother who died decades ago, the NCIS team searches for the perpetrator, as Ducky recalls the final emotional days he had with his sibling. Also, with the holidays approaching, ', 13, 11, '15 Dec. 2015'),
(1420, 'tt5276664', 15, 'Sister City: Part 1', 'MV5BNTg3NTcxMzEzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzU5ODQ2NzE@', 'Gibbs and his team work with Pride and the New Orleans team to find Abby''s brother and figure out why the passengers and crew of a private plane he catered were poisoned.', 13, 12, '5 Jan. 2016'),
(1421, 'tt5302808', 15, 'Déjà Vu', 'MV5BOTQ4NjQ2NDI3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODE4NTk3NzE@', 'The investigation of a seaman''s murder uncovers the resurface of a human-trafficking ring, while McGee hopes to spend the night with a colleague during a power outage.', 13, 13, '19 Jan. 2016'),
(1422, 'tt5378664', 15, 'Decompressed', '01', 'Add a Plot', 13, 14, '9 Feb. 2016'),
(1423, 'tt4917582', 17, 'Unauthorized Magic', 'MV5BMTg5NDg5OTYzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzM4NzE4NzE@', 'A smart, geeky and socially awkward young man is amazed to realize that Magic he''s so passionate about is actually real, when he''s unexpectedly invited to attend a college of magic in New York.', 1, 1, '16 Dec. 2015'),
(1424, 'tt4976372', 17, 'The Source of Magic', 'MV5BNTg4ODgwMjQ5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzU4NzE4NzE@', 'Quentin is distraught as he faces expulsion for his involvement in an otherworldly attack on Brakebills, while Julia delves deeper into underground magic and takes a test to prove herself to the Hedge Witches.', 1, 2, '25 Jan. 2016'),
