(1557, 'tt3252298', 20, 'The Well', 'MV5BMTY5OTU0MDAxMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM3MzIzMjE@', 'Ward becomes exposed to a piece of an Asgardian staff, which causes his worst memory to resurface.', 1, 8, '19 Nov. 2013'),
(1558, 'tt3252332', 20, 'Repairs', 'MV5BMzg1NjI1OTU5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzU3MzIzMjE@', 'The agents investigate the strange occurrences of a woman who, they believe, has telekinetic powers.', 1, 9, '26 Nov. 2013'),
(1559, 'tt3252318', 20, 'The Bridge', 'MV5BNTUwOTcxMDc4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTk2MzIzMjE@', 'S.H.I.E.L.D. receives assistance from Mike Peterson as they take on Centipede once again.', 1, 10, '10 Dec. 2013'),
(1560, 'tt3307564', 20, 'The Magical Place', 'MV5BMTA1NzQzMDY5NTFeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDg5MDQyMzIx', 'S.H.I.E.L.D. organizes a full scale hunt for Coulson. Centipede tries to resurface the memories on what happened after Coulson died.', 1, 11, '7 Jan. 2014'),
(1561, 'tt3307568', 20, 'Seeds', 'MV5BMTQ1OTg5MTU2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjkwNDIzMjE@', 'While investigating a problem at S.H.I.E.L.D. Academy, Coulson and May turn up unexpected information about Skye''s parents.', 1, 12, '14 Jan. 2014'),
(1562, 'tt3307566', 20, 'T.R.A.C.K.S.', 'MV5BMTUxMzQzOTM0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTgwNDIzMjE@', 'The team tries to confiscate an important device on a train, but when one agent takes a very risky move that backfires, the entire team is affected.', 1, 13, '4 Feb. 2014'),
(1563, 'tt3476430', 20, 'T.A.H.I.T.I.', 'MV5BMjg4MTE2OTA1Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjQ1MzIyMTE@', 'Coulson and the team rush to Bethesda in an attempt to save Skye''s life.', 1, 14, '4 Mar. 2014'),
(1564, 'tt3473818', 20, 'Yes Men', 'MV5BMjM5MjY2NDI2OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjI0NzEzMTE@', 'While Skye recovers, Lady Sif arrives with need of assistance in capturing an escaped Asgardian prisoner, named Lorelei.', 1, 15, '11 Mar. 2014'),
(1565, 'tt3539224', 20, 'End of the Beginning', 'MV5BMTQ0NzI5MTQ0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjEwMzEzMjE@', 'Agent Garett and Triplett have returned to assist Coulson''s team hunt down S.H.I.E.L.D.''s devious nemesis--the Clairvoyant. But will Deathlok kill them all to guard his master''s identity?', 1, 16, '1 Apr. 2014'),
(1566, 'tt3539406', 20, 'Turn, Turn, Turn', 'MV5BMjA1NTA0NDE3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDcwMzEzMjE@', 'S.H.I.E.L.D. has been compromised by an old enemy. The team doesn''t know whom to trust.', 1, 17, '8 Apr. 2014'),
(1567, 'tt3609126', 20, 'Providence', 'MV5BMTExNjg5NDczNDReQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDEwMTg4NTEx', 'With Colonel Glenn Talbot now on their trail, Coulson and his team seek refuge in the last place anyone would look, where they begin to uncover S.H.I.E.L.D.''S most dangerous secrets -- secrets that could destroy them all.', 1, 18, '15 Apr. 2014'),
(1568, 'tt3609154', 20, 'The Only Light in the Darkness', 'MV5BMTAzMDUzOTA3OTReQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDg5MjYxMzIx', 'Agent Koenig puts the team through the ultimate lie detector test and Coulson races to protect an old flame from an old enemy.', 1, 19, '22 Apr. 2014'),
(1569, 'tt3609164', 20, 'Nothing Personal', 'MV5BNDMwMTMwOTcyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkwNzc2MTE@', 'Just when there''s no one left to trust, Agent Maria Hill returns to team up with Coulson as S.H.I.E.L.D. is being destroyed around them.', 1, 20, '29 Apr. 2014'),
(1570, 'tt3609168', 20, 'Ragtag', 'MV5BMjk2OTAyMTYzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjgyODI3MTE@', 'Ward''s betrayal and HYDRA''s shocking secrets are revealed as Coulson''s team goes undercover on a mission that leaves no one unscathed.', 1, 21, '6 May 2014'),
(1571, 'tt3609170', 20, 'Beginning of the End', 'MV5BMTUzOTQ1MzMyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM2OTg3MTE@', 'Dark secrets are revealed as Coulson and his team put everything on the line to stop Garrett and the forces of HYDRA.', 1, 22, '13 May 2014'),
(1572, 'tt3721000', 20, 'Shadows', 'MV5BMjUzNzI1MDQ3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzE3NDc2MjE@', 'Carl Creel is sent after an item that was stolen from Hydra during WWII. Fitz tries to cope with his mental issues.', 2, 1, '23 Sep. 2014'),
(1573, 'tt3997450', 20, 'Heavy Is the Head', 'MV5BMTU0MDI3NjgxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDkzNDE4MjE@', 'Hunter gets captured by General Talbot. May goes after Creel and the Obelisk.', 2, 2, '30 Sep. 2014'),
(1574, 'tt3997456', 20, 'Making Friends and Influencing People', 'MV5BNTY0ODYyMjIxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI0NDE4MjE@', 'Simmons is forced to help Hydra capture Donnie Gill. S.H.I.E.L.D. tries to get to him first.', 2, 3, '7 Oct. 2014'),
(1575, 'tt3997452', 20, 'Face My Enemy', 'MV5BMjE1OTY0NTEyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQ2NTIwMzE@', 'When May gets kidnapped, Hydra sends out an impersonator to lure Coulson into a trap. Fitz tries to find the confidence to join the rest of the team in their social activities.', 2, 4, '14 Oct. 2014');
