(1576, 'tt3970174', 20, 'A Hen in the Wolf House', 'MV5BMjI0ODc4MzU2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzEwNjIxMzE@', 'Raina threatens to expose Simmons to Hydra unless Coulson hands Skye over to her father.', 2, 5, '21 Oct. 2014'),
(1577, 'tt4078580', 20, 'A Fractured House', 'MV5BMTYwODY5NTM3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY4OTcxMzE@', 'The world turns against S.H.I.E.L.D. when Hydra impersonates them to attack The United Nations, and an unexpected enemy leads the charge to bring about their downfall.', 2, 6, '28 Oct. 2014'),
(1578, 'tt4082652', 20, 'The Writing on the Wall', 'MV5BNjk2NTMyOTQwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjc3OTE0MzE@', 'A mysterious man is killing off former S.H.I.E.L.D. agents and carving the same markings as Coulson. Coulson tries to track him down. Meanwhile, May leads a team on a manhunt for Ward.', 2, 7, '11 Nov. 2014'),
(1579, 'tt4082656', 20, 'The Things We Bury', 'MV5BMTEzMDgwODY2NTheQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDYzMDg0NDMx', 'Coulson and team find themselves in an epic face-off against Hydra to uncover an ancient secret, while Ward kidnaps his brother, Senator Christian Ward, for a violent trip down memory lane.', 2, 8, '18 Nov. 2014'),
(1580, 'tt4120698', 20, 'Ye Who Enter Here', 'MV5BMjA4MTc0NTAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTkyOTA2MzE@', 'While Coulson''s team tries to find the entrance to the mysterious alien city, the rest of the agents try to rescue Raina when they find out that Hydra is after her.', 2, 9, '2 Dec. 2014'),
(1581, 'tt4120702', 20, 'What They Become', 'MV5BMTg3NDA1ODc1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTAyOTA2MzE@', 'Whitehall and Coulson''s forces take part in an explosive confrontation that changes everyone. Skye uncovers some truths about her past.', 2, 10, '9 Dec. 2014'),
(1582, 'tt4120704', 20, 'Aftershocks', 'MV5BMTkwMjI1MTYxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjg5MDk1NDE@', 'Coulson and the team are faced with the consequences of the war with Hydra. As revelations threaten to destroy them, Hydra makes a move.', 2, 11, '3 Mar. 2015'),
(1583, 'tt4120714', 20, 'Who You Really Are', 'MV5BMTQ4MDQwMDk4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTAxMzY3NDE@', 'Coulson and the team help a confused Lady Sif, who has lost her memory after a battle with a mysterious warrior.', 2, 12, '10 Mar. 2015'),
(1584, 'tt4120718', 20, 'One of Us', 'MV5BMjI3ODA0NTA3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTU2NTE5NDE@', 'Cal wants vengeance, so he rallies a team of super villains to crush S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile, May turns to her ex-husband, Dr. Andrew Garner, to help with a crisis threatening the harmony of the team.', 2, 13, '17 Mar. 2015'),
(1585, 'tt4120720', 20, 'Love in the Time of Hydra', 'MV5BMTQyODE3MTc0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIwMjgwNTE@', 'The team are bewildered by a recent shocking revelation as they face a difficult decision. Meanwhile, Bobbi and Mack declare their loyalty to Hunter; and Ward and Agent 33 take care of a private matter.', 2, 14, '24 Mar. 2015'),
(1586, 'tt4120722', 20, 'One Door Closes', 'MV5BNjA0MzE1Mzc1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAwNjIxNTE@', 'War comes to Coulson''s doorstep in a way he never anticipated as shocking revelations are brought to light, and Skye struggles to control her new abilities but will soon make a decision that irrevocably changes her life.', 2, 15, '31 Mar. 2015'),
(1587, 'tt4120726', 20, 'Afterlife', 'MV5BMTYxNjcwMjIxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODAxMjIyNTE@', 'As Robert Gonzalez makes his move, Coulson must do whatever it takes to protect the future of S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile Skye''s journey to control her powers take a surprising turn when she meets the enigmatic Inhuman named Lincoln.', 2, 16, '7 Apr. 2015'),
(1588, 'tt4120730', 20, 'Melinda', 'MV5BMjIzMjY3MDE0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTI0NTMzNTE@', 'The story of Melinda May''s transformation into "The Cavalry" is revealed as she finds herself at a crossroads in the war between Coulson and Gonzales. As Skye learns more about her true heritage from Lincoln, the truth about Inhumans will send her in a ne', 2, 17, '14 Apr. 2015'),
(1589, 'tt4120738', 20, 'Frenemy of My Enemy', 'MV5BMjI3NDM3ODM0NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzEwMzI0NTE@', 'A dangerous new alliance is formed as Coulson and Hunter turn to the last person anyone would expect, Grant Ward! As the war between S.H.I.E.L.D. factions continues, Skye and Lincoln will find themselves drawn into this conflict.', 2, 18, '21 Apr. 2015'),
