(2564, 'tt1982341', 28, 'The Best Man', 'MV5BNjIzMzYyMDkzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjIxMDYzNg@@', 'While Barney prepares for his wedding to a mystery bride, he and Ted reminisce about Punchy''s wedding, including when Marshall and Lily announced they were having a baby. Meanwhile, Robin considers telling Barney she has feelings for him.', 7, 1, '19 Sep. 2011'),
(2565, 'tt2039807', 28, 'The Naked Truth', 'MV5BMTc2OTQyNjA4Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTA4MDMyMjE@', 'Ted tries to choose a date for the Architect''s Ball, an embarrassing Internet video could cost Marshall a new job, and Barney makes a bold move to prove to Nora that he''s a changed man.', 7, 2, '19 Sep. 2011'),
(2566, 'tt2049132', 28, 'Ducky Tie', 'MV5BOTI5ODgwOTA1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzA0NzI4Ng@@', 'At the Architect''s Ball, Ted runs into Victoria, who tells him that she''s getting married. Meanwhile, Barney places an unlikely wager with Marshall and Lily in order to see Lily''s breasts.', 7, 3, '26 Sep. 2011'),
(2567, 'tt2049980', 28, 'The Stinson Missile Crisis', 'MV5BMjEyNTU4OTQyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTQ0NzI4Ng@@', 'Jealous over Barney''s relationship with Nora, Robin tells her court-appointed therapist the series of events that led up to the assault that she committed.', 7, 4, '3 Oct. 2011'),
(2568, 'tt2071800', 28, 'Field Trip', 'MV5BNDI1NjE4OTI2Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTU3MDMyMjE@', 'Robin tries to date her therapist, Marshall thinks his boss has gone soft on environmentalism, Barney suspects that Nora may be lying about her age, and Ted takes his Intro to Architecture class on the worst field trip ever.', 7, 5, '10 Oct. 2011'),
(2569, 'tt2072524', 28, 'Mystery vs. History', 'MV5BNjY3NDg2NzEyOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjU5MDMyMjE@', 'Ted agrees to go on a date without researching each other on the Internet beforehand, Barney urges Marshall and Lily to find out and reveal the gender of their child, and Kevin tries but fails to avoid passing judgment on the group.', 7, 6, '17 Oct. 2011'),
(2570, 'tt2072525', 28, 'Noretta', 'MV5BMTg5NTk4Mjk4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODM5MDMyMjE@', 'Kevin''s declaration that everybody marries their parents ruins Marshall and Lily''s romantic evening, but will anything keep Barney from getting lucky with Nora? And will Kevin finally get fed up with Ted and Robin''s close relationship?', 7, 7, '24 Oct. 2011'),
(2571, 'tt2072526', 28, 'The Slutty Pumpkin Returns', 'MV5BMjM1MjUxMTg5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ5MDMyMjE@', 'Ted finds his long lost crush from a Halloween party 10 years ago, but will there be any chemistry? Meanwhile, Lily''s "pregnancy brain" convinces her to move to the suburbs, and Barney finds out he''s one-quarter Canadian.', 7, 8, '31 Oct. 2011'),
(2572, 'tt2094413', 28, 'Disaster Averted', 'MV5BNDAwMjg4NjEzN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDM3MDMyMjE@', 'The gang explains to Kevin the origins of the "No boogie-boarding" sign in front of McClaren''s, which has to do with hurricane Irene. Meanwhile, Barney negotiates with Marshall about how to get out of wearing the ducky tie.', 7, 9, '7 Nov. 2011'),
(2573, 'tt2102769', 28, 'Tick Tick Tick', 'MV5BNzM2NTc5MzkyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODg2MDUwNw@@', 'Barney and Robin are afraid to break the news to Nora and Kevin that they cheated with each other and want to get back together, while Ted and Marshall get stoned together at a concert.', 7, 10, '14 Nov. 2011'),
