(2576, 'tt2157459', 28, 'Tailgate', 'MV5BMjAwMjgwMjY4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDYzODAyNw@@', 'After celebrating New Year''s Eve, Marshall visits his father''s graveside to carry on their tradition of tailgating. Meanwhile, Barney and Ted open a bar called "Puzzles," and Robin is forced to fill in for an inebriated news anchor.', 7, 13, '2 Jan. 2012'),
