(2608, 'tt2815916', 28, 'Romeward Bound', 'MV5BMTQ3MjAwMTU0Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODYxMDgzOQ@@', '"The Captain" offers Lily a job in Rome, but will she take it? Meanwhile, Ted won''t stop raving about the body of Barney and Robin''s wedding planner.', 8, 21, '15 Apr. 2013'),
