(2612, 'tt2802532', 28, 'The Locket', 'MV5BMTg0NDMzMjM0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODk4ODAwMDE@', 'Lily meets an interesting person on the train to Farhampton, Marshall gets kicked off his flight to New York, Barney and Robin discover that they might be related, and Ted prepares to deliver a personal gift to Robin.', 9, 1, '23 Sep. 2013'),
