(3771, 'tt1054726', 49, 'Cancer Man', 'MV5BODg5MTYzNzM4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDAwOTc5MjE@', 'Walt tells the rest of his family about his cancer. Jesse tries to make amends with his own parents.', 1, 4, '17 Feb. 2008'),
