(3796, 'tt1615558', 49, 'Kafkaesque', 'MV5BMTc2NjA4OTYyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMDg5MjE@', 'Skyler hatches a plan as Hank''s hospital bills stack up. Meanwhile, Walt and Gus come to a better understanding as Jesse, looking for more independence, pursues a new opportunity.', 3, 9, '16 May 2010'),
