(3798, 'tt1615551', 49, 'Abiquiu', 'MV5BMTU5OTAxNTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYxMDg5MjE@', 'Skyler gets more involved in Walt''s business, much to his chagrin as Hank struggles with his recovery. Meanwhile, Jesse takes an active role in his new enterprise, leading him to a startling discovery.', 3, 11, '30 May 2010'),
(3799, 'tt1615552', 49, 'Half Measures', 'MV5BMTM2NzA0MTExMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjczOTQ1Mw@@', 'Against Walt''s advice, Jesse lashes out. Fearing for Jesse''s safety, Walt takes drastic action to intervene. Meanwhile a tragic event leads to a shocking confrontation.', 3, 12, '6 Jun. 2010'),
(3800, 'tt1615553', 49, 'Full Measure', 'MV5BMTM1Njc3OTkwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTkyMDY1Mw@@', 'Jesse has disappeared and Walt is in big trouble with Gus. So Gus rehires Gale to learn from Walt''s cooking so that they can dispose of Walt once and for all.', 3, 13, '13 Jun. 2010'),
(3801, 'tt1683084', 49, 'Box Cutter', 'MV5BMTA2NzQzODA3OTdeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDY3NjU2NzU@', 'Walt and Jesse are held captive for Gus, after Gale''s death. Meanwhile, Skyler tries to find out what happened to Walt.', 4, 1, '17 Jul. 2011'),
(3802, 'tt1683089', 49, 'Thirty-Eight Snub', 'MV5BMTQ4NTM1OTI1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg5OTc5MjE@', 'Walt attempts to form a new alliance as he plans his next move. Meanwhile Skyler pushes Walt towards a business opportunity, in hopes of protecting the family.', 4, 2, '24 Jul. 2011'),
(3803, 'tt1683090', 49, 'Open House', 'MV5BNzg1MTcxMDI2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjE1MDMxNg@@', 'While Walt worries about Gus''s interference and Jesse''s increasingly fragile state of mind, Skyler steps up the pressure to get what she wants.', 4, 3, '31 Jul. 2011'),
(3804, 'tt1683091', 49, 'Bullet Points', 'MV5BMTU2NzIyNjMyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODc5OTc5MjE@', 'As Skyler concocts an elaborate story to explain the Whites'' finances, a worried Walt discovers that Hank has begun a new investigation.', 4, 4, '7 Aug. 2011'),
(3805, 'tt1683092', 49, 'Shotgun', 'MV5BMjE4NDM3MzkzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjEzODcyNg@@', 'Jesse rides shotgun with Mike on a perilous run of pickups, prompting Walt to worry that his partner is about to be killed.', 4, 5, '14 Aug. 2011'),
(3806, 'tt1683093', 49, 'Cornered', 'MV5BMjE2NTQ1MDQ5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg5OTc5MjE@', 'Skyler adopts an aloof approach when she suspects that Walt isn''t telling her the truth. Meanwhile, Jesse proves his worth to Mike and Gus.', 4, 6, '21 Aug. 2011'),
(3807, 'tt1683094', 49, 'Problem Dog', 'MV5BMjMyODYwNDQ5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDg5OTc5MjE@', 'Ordered to return the car he bought for his son, Walt strikes back by putting Skyler in a tough spot with their new money-laundering operation.', 4, 7, '28 Aug. 2011'),
(3808, 'tt1683095', 49, 'Hermanos', 'MV5BMTQxMzk0ODkwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjc5OTc5MjE@', 'When Hank produces evidence that Gus is Albuquerque''s crystal meth kingpin, Walt worries that he and Jesse will be killed to protect their boss.', 4, 8, '4 Sep. 2011'),
(3809, 'tt1683096', 49, 'Bug', 'MV5BMTQ0MTA3NTIxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDEwODE2Ng@@', 'While Walt tries to subvert Hank''s probe into the Albuquerque meth scene, a deadly warning forces Gus to consider a deal with the cartel.', 4, 9, '11 Sep. 2011'),
(3810, 'tt1683085', 49, 'Salud', 'MV5BMTAwNDg2MjY5NjBeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDg2NzAwNzY@', 'Jesse, Gus, and Mike fly down to Mexico, and Jesse cooks the blue meth for the cartel. Walt misses his son''s 16th birthday after his fight with Jesse.', 4, 10, '18 Sep. 2011'),
(3811, 'tt1683086', 49, 'Crawl Space', 'MV5BMTMzMTgzNzY4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTM5Nzc3Ng@@', 'Hank asks Walt to drive him to the laundry where the meth lab is hidden. Ted still won''t pay the IRS so Skyler asks Saul for help, and Saul sends in his A-Team. Gus and Jesse return from Mexico, and Walt fears he is in trouble with Gus.', 4, 11, '25 Sep. 2011'),
(3812, 'tt1683087', 49, 'End Times', 'MV5BMzcwNzM5MDQ4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODc4MzU4Ng@@', 'The DEA is putting Hank and his family in protective custody; however, Walt refuses and awaits his fate in his house. Meanwhile, Brock has fallen terribly ill and Jesse suspects Walt may be behind it.', 4, 12, '2 Oct. 2011'),
(3813, 'tt1683088', 49, 'Face Off', 'MV5BMTkzMDU5MTcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTI2NTg4Ng@@', 'Jesse is brought to the FBI for questioning on his knowledge of Ricin. In a last effort to kill Gus, Walt must ask for help from an old enemy.', 4, 13, '9 Oct. 2011'),
(3814, 'tt2081647', 49, 'Live Free or Die', 'MV5BMjIwMzc0Mjk2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODM5NzY5Nw@@', 'Now that Gus is dead, Walt, Jesse, and Mike work to cover their tracks. Skyler panics when Ted Beneke wakes up.', 5, 1, '15 Jul. 2012'),
(3815, 'tt2301457', 49, 'Madrigal', 'MV5BNTc5NjQ0MTQwN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDk2MzQxOA@@', 'Walt and Jesse pursue an unlikely business partner; the DEA follows new leads.', 5, 2, '22 Jul. 2012'),
